2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28191251%2Fimage-1179.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Japanese%20companies%20told%20the%20visiting%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Yoshimasa%20Hayashi%2C%20that%20they%20want%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20predictable%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctransparent%E2%80%9D%20business%20environment%20in%20India%2C%20even%20as%20Tokyo%20said%20that%20it%20was%20up%20to%20India%20as%20the%20G20%20president%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20language%20over%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20joint%20communique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20foreign%20minister%20arrived%20in%20India%20on%20July%2028%2C%20Friday%20and%20chaired%20a%20Strategic%20Dialogue%20with%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar.%20On%20Friday%20morning%2C%20the%20two%20ministers%20took%20part%20in%20a%20public%20interaction%20at%20the%20India-Japan%20Forum.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20lunch%20meeting%20with%20representatives%20of%20Japanese%20companies%20and%20the%20Japan%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20briefing%20for%20the%20Indian%20press%2C%20Japanese%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20press%20secretary%2C%20Yukiko%20Okano%2C%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cview%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Japanese%20firms%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20more%20predictable%2C%20stable%20and%20transparent%20business%20environment%E2%80%9D%2C%20especially%20related%20to%20regulatory%20and%20tax%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20while%20this%20was%20not%20discussed%20on%20Friday%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20have%20also%20heard%20that%20infrastructure%20challenges%20were%20raised%20in%20the%20past%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20spokesperson%20noted%20that%20the%20business%20chambers%20had%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20Indian%20authorities%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Japanese%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20on%20the%20Strategic%20Dialogue%20had%20said%20that%20minister%20Hayashi%20had%20%E2%80%9Crequested%20cooperation%20to%20improve%20the%20investment%20environment%20and%20for%20the%20early%20establishment%20of%20a%20Joint%20Crediting%20Mechanism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Japanese%20figures%2C%20Japan%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20fifth%20largest%20investor%20in%202021.%20There%20are%20around%201%2C439%20Japanese%20firms%20having%20presence%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Japanese%20prime%20minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%E2%80%99s%20visit%20last%20year%2C%20a%20target%20of%20public%20and%20private%20investment%20of%20five%20trillion%20yen%20in%20India%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20till%202027%20was%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOkano%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Csteady%E2%80%9D%20progress%20in%20meeting%20the%20target%2C%20but%20added%20that%20both%20sides%20were%20not%20releasing%20yearly%20figures%20on%20that%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsouth-korean-firms-havent-received-the-promised-incentives-as-part-of-pli-scheme-says-top-official%5C%22%3ECentre%20Accused%20of%20%E2%80%98Unfairly%E2%80%99%20Withholding%20Production%20Incentives%20to%20South%20Korean%20Firms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20discussions%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20on%20which%20India%20and%20Japan%20have%20varying%20positions%2C%20the%20Japanese%20diplomat%20said%20that%20both%20countries%20share%20%E2%80%9Cfundamental%20principles%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Cterritorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%20should%20be%20protected%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20use%20of%20force%20to%20change%20status%20quo%20%E2%80%9Cis%20not%20permissible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reminded%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20good%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Ukrainian%20president%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20G7%20summit%20hosted%20by%20Japan%20in%20Hiroshima.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20Japan%20wants%20Zelensky%20to%20participate%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20okay%20either%20way%20on%20whether%20India%20invites%20Zelensky.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20language%20of%20the%20joint%20communique%20is%20still%20under%20discussion%20between%20the%20G20%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20G7%20will%20not%20dilute%20their%20position%20on%20Ukraine%20irrespective%20of%20the%20forum%2C%20the%20Japanese%20deputy%20press%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20joint%20communique%2C%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20up%20to%20the%20president%20on%20how%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-ukraine-russia-criticise%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20India%20Unable%20to%20Criticise%20the%20Country%20That%20Has%20Invaded%20Ukraine%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20speaking%20at%20the%20India-Japan%20forum%2C%20Hayashi%20said%20that%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20many%20pressing%20challenges%2C%20including%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20Japan%20and%20India%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20share%20the%20necessity%20to%20lead%20the%20world%20to%20cooperation%2C%20rather%20than%20to%20division%20and%20confrontation%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20free%20and%20open%20international%20order%20based%20on%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20key%20to%20realising%20such%20a%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20India%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindispensable%E2%80%9D%20partner%20in%20achieving%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20Hayashi%20said%20%E2%80%9Cfree%E2%80%9D%20means%20each%20country%20is%20free%20to%20make%20decisions%20based%20on%20its%20own%20sovereignty%20and%20%E2%80%9Copen%E2%80%9D%20means%20respect%20for%20principles%2C%20including%20inclusiveness%2C%20openness%20and%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20vital%20that%20we%20refrain%20from%20imposing%20values%20or%20excluding%20certain%20countries.%20This%20concept%20is%20especially%20crucial%20for%20smaller%20countries.%20In%20coordination%20with%20India%2C%20Japan%20intends%20to%20materialise%20such%20a%20concept%20through%20realising%20a%20%E2%80%98Free%20and%20Open%20Indo-Pacific%E2%80%99%20or%20FOIP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20prime%20minister%20will%20be%20back%20in%20India%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20year%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690552839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28191251%2Fimage-1179.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fduring-japan-fms-visit-japanese-firms-lobby-for-a-better-business-environment-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tokyo%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20up%20to%20India%20as%20the%20G20%20president%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20language%20over%20Ukraine%20for%20a%20joint%20communique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fduring-japan-fms-visit-japanese-firms-lobby-for-a-better-business-environment-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Rejects%20Cousin's%20Marriage%20Proposal%2C%20He%20Kills%20Her%20With%20Iron%20Rod%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20battered%20his%20cousin%20to%20death%20with%20an%20iron%20rod%20in%20Delhi%20allegedly%20because%20she%20had%20refused%20to%20marry%20him%2C%20and%20he%20was%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20anyone%20else%20to%20agree%20either.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20who%20killed%20the%2025-year-old%20in%20a%20park%20this%20afternoon%2C%20had%20allegedly%20been%20planning%20the%20murder%20for%20three%20days%20and%20surrendered%20to%20the%20police%20hours%20after%20committing%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20received%20information%20that%20the%20body%20of%20a%2025-year-old%20girl%20was%20found%20in%20a%20park%20near%20Aurobindo%20College%20in%20South%20Delhi's%20Malviya%20Nagar.%20An%20iron%20rod%20was%20found%20near%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20victim's%20name%20was%20Nargis%20and%20she%20had%20been%20spotted%20in%20the%20park%20with%20a%20man%20named%20Irfan%2C%20who%20was%20her%20cousin.%20Police%20found%20that%20Nargis%20was%20attending%20a%20stenographer's%20course%20in%20Malviya%20Nagar%20and%20had%20completed%20her%20studies%20from%20Kamala%20Nehru%20College%20earlier%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22f0427u4%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ff0427u4_delhi-park-murder-nargis-650_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20police%20were%20probing%20the%20case%20further%2C%20Irfan%20surrendered%20before%20them%20and%20was%20taken%20into%20custody.%20During%20his%20interrogation%2C%20Irfan%2C%20who%20is%2028%20and%20works%20as%20a%20food%20delivery%20agent%2C%20told%20the%20police%20that%20Nargis'%20mother%20and%20his%20mother%20are%20sisters.%20He%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20marry%20Nargis%20but%20her%20family%20had%20refused%2C%20partly%20because%20he%20did%20not%20have%20a%20proper%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENargis%20also%20refused%20to%20marry%20him%20and%20stopped%20speaking%20to%20him%20or%20answering%20his%20calls.%20Irfan%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20disturbed%20and%20angry%20about%20this%2C%20and%20his%20anger%20was%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20one%20else%20was%20agreeing%20to%20marry%2