ge%20dump%20yards%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20facing%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20environmental%20pollution.%20We%20would%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20and%20seeing%20its%20condition%20just%20shook%20me.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20seeing%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20chip%20packets%20there%3B%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20there%20was%20humongous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagyashree%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20has%2078%20lakh%20MT%20of%20waste%20and%20reached%20its%20saturation%20point%20in%202002.%20Yet%2C%20700%20MT%20of%20waste%20is%20dumped%20there%20daily.%20Work%20is%20underway%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20to%20flatten%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20recycling%20her%20life%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201328px)%20100vw%2C%201328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%201328w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-500x280.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-768x431.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325579%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%20by%20TDC%E2%80%99s%20workers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagyashree%20interacted%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20understand%20what%20happens%20to%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20most%20of%20the%20waste%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20recycled%3B%20it%20was%20just%20incinerated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20weren%E2%80%99t%20a%20lot%20of%20recycling%20units%20then.%20While%20looking%20at%20options%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20plastic%20menace%2C%20I%20met%20someone%20who%20wanted%20to%20establish%20a%20recycling%20unit%20in%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20helped%20him%20set%20up%20the%20unit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycling%20unit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Bhagyashree%20learnt%20a%20lot%20about%20plastic%20recycling.%20She%20went%20to%20various%20exhibitions%20to%20see%20the%20different%20recycling%20machines%20used%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMachines%20used%20in%20Germany%20and%20China%20would%20segregate%20the%20waste%2C%20but%20those%20machines%20could%20not%20process%20the%20type%20of%20waste%20we%20produced.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20segregate%20and%20clean%20the%20waste%20properly%20before%20using%20the%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20set%20up%20small%20segregation%20systems%20and%20tweaked%20the%20machinery%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20waste%20they%20needed%20to%20recycle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20local%20recyclers%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20like%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20Whirlpool%2C%20and%20Arvind%20Mills%20to%20establish%20efficient%20in-house%20plastic%20waste%20management%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20different%20kinds%20of%20plastic%2C%20its%20nature%2C%20qualities%20and%20recyclability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20learnings%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20her%20startup%2C%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(TDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELove%20for%20skincare%20turned%20into%20a%20business%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201113px)%20100vw%2C%201113px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221113%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plastic%20waste%20being%20processed%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%201113w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-300x192.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-500x320.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-768x491.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325576%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlastic%20waste%20is%20recycled%20by%20TDC%20in%20partnership%20with%20recyclers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202020%2C%20Bhagyashree%20moved%20to%20Rajasthan%20after%20getting%20married.%20In%20Jaipur%2C%20she%20again%20started%20consulting%20with%20the%20government%20on%20ways%20to%20manage%20waste%20better.%20But%20a%20month%20later%2C%20the%20nation%20went%20under%20lockdown.%20COVID%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20deal%20with%20waste%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20with%20the%20local%20pollution%20control%20board%20during%20the%20lockdown.%20With%20the%20addition%20of%20used%20masks%20and%20gloves%2C%20we%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20ways%20to%20segregate%20contaminated%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20also%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20D2C%20(direct-to-consumer)%20brands%2C%20including%20skincare.%20Newly%20married%2C%20she%20says%20she%20loved%20trying%20on%20different%20skincare%20products.%20But%20while%20others%20focussed%20on%20the%20product%2C%20Bhagyashree%20focused%20on%20the%20packaging!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20see%20a%20new%20brand%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20catches%20my%20eye%20is%20the%20packaging.%20Almost%20100%20new%20brands%20have%20come%20up%2C%20and%20most%20FMCG%20(fast-moving%20consumer%20goods)%20brands%20use%20low-value%20packaging.%20I%20was%20horrified%20at%20the%20waste%20we%20are%20accumulating%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%20Mumbai-based%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311038%2Fmani-vajipey-raj-madangopal-banyan-nation-hyderabad-recycle-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-bottles-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20by%20so%20many%20new%20brands%20with%20new%20types%20of%20packaging%20gave%20her%20sleepless%20nights.%20This%20led%20her%20to%20start%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20in%20November%202020%20to%20%E2%80%9Creduce%20waste%2C%20revive%20lives%20and%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20is%20a%20plastic%20credit%20platform%20that%20helps%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(%40thedisposalcompany)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20startups%20to%20do%20this%20in%20India%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20the%20first-mover%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Disposal%20Company%20neutralises%20the%20plastic%20waste%20generated%20by%20a%20brand%20by%20recovering%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20plastic%20from%20landfills%20and%20recycling%20it.%20We%20then%20report%20it%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20Bhagyashree%20says%20they%20first%20educate%20brands%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20their%20packaging%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20wherever%20possible.%20They%20work%20with%20design%20labs%20to%20do%20so.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ideal%20thing%20is%20to%20reduce%20plastic.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20brands%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%2C%20or%20their%20products%20can%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20in%20other%20forms%20of%20packaging.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20we%20help%20them%20reduce%20their%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%2070%20brands%20across%20India%2C%20Singapore%20and%20the%20UK.%20Its%20clients%20include%20companies%20like%20mCaffeine%2C%20Slurrp%20Farm%2C%20The%20Souled%20Store%2C%20Bombay%20Shaving%20Company%2C%20Blue%20Tokai%20Coffee%2C%20and%20SLAY%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20collaborates%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20training%20and%20support%20to%20improve%20waste%20workers%E2%80%99%20skills.%20We%20also%20give%20them%20proper%20safety%20gear.%20We%20have%20provided%20jobs%20to%20500%20such%20waste%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bhagyashree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20TDC%20knows%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20neutralised%2C%20they%20retrieve%20that%20much%20waste%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfills%20with%20the%20help%20of%20rag%20pickers.%20Once%20retrieved%2C%20they%20segregate%20the%20plastic%20and%20send%20it%20to%20recyclers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%20recycling%20companies%20like%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20recycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20granules.%20We%20sell%20these%20granules%20to%20companies%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20sustainable%20products%20like%20photo%20frames%2C%20toys%20etc.%20Mixed%20plastic%2C%20which%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%2C%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20plant%20that%20converts%20it%20to%20energy.%20We%20recycle%20about%2060%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20per%20month.%2020%E2%80%9325%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20credit%20is%20given%20to%20TDC%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sanyam%20Jain%20of%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20better%20planet%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201196px)%20100vw%2C%201196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waste%20being%20picked%20up%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%201196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-300x167.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-500x278.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-768x427.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-150x83.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325578%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlastic%20waste%20is%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20by%20a%20TDC%20worker%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20helps%20in%20recycling%2045%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste%20per%20month.%20The%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20though%2C%20reflects%20the%20founder.%20It%20took%20her%20seven%20months%20to%20get%20the%20first%20client%20%E2%80%94%20mCaffeine.%20What%20kept%20her%20motivated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20buy%20a%20milk%20packet%20or%20carton%2C%20I%20think%20about%20the%20microplastics%20in%20it.%20My%20mother%20is%20a%20cancer%20survivor.%20There%20is%20a%20probability%20of%20me%20getting%20cancer%20too.%20Consuming%20microplastics%20can%20further%20add%20to%20our%20woes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisphenol%20A%20(BPA)%20is%20a%20chemical%20used%20in%20several%20plastic%20products%20and%20packaging.%20An%20%3Cem%3ENCBI%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20many%20studies%20have%20confirmed%20that%20BPA%20is%20associated%20with%20obesity%2C%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20reproductive%20disorder%2C%20and%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20having%20a%20child%20in%20the%20future%2C%20these%20thoughts%20worry%20me.%20I%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323368%2Fsonika-bhasin-sustainable-mom-lifestyle-plastic-free-july-composting-bioenzyme-cloth-diaper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20a%20better%20planet%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20our%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThoughts%20like%20these%20keep%20Bhagyashree%2C%20who%20is%20today%20an%20%E2%80%9Cenvironmental%2C%20social%2C%20and%20corporate%20governance%20(ESG)%20consultant%E2%80%9D%2C%20going.%20She%20urges%20not%20just%20businesses%20but%20everyone%20to%20think%20about%20what%20they%20are%20consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20conscious%20consumerism.%20Ask%20the%20brands%20you%20buy%20from%20about%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20for%20the%20environment.%20Hold%20them%20accountable%20and%20they%20will%20start%20taking%20action.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20also%20take%20small%20steps%20in%20your%20daily%20life%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7068600%2F%23B30-ijerph-17-01212%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENCBI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fwaste-processing-at-ghazipur-landfill-yet-to-pick-up-pace%2Farticle66785760.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Waste%20processing%20at%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20yet%20to%20pick%20up%20pace%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Muneef%20Khan%20for%20The%20Hindu%2C%20Published%20on%2001%20May%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690551389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali%20started%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20to%20help%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste%20by%20recycling%20an%20equal%20amount.%20It%20works%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20in%20Delhi%20who%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste%20from%20Ghazipur%20landfills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No-Trust%20Motion%20Waiting%2C%20LS%20Passes%203%20Bills%20in%2030%20Minutes%3B%20'Unconstitutional%2C'%20Says%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28190125%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-6.59.30-PM_cleanup-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20July%2028%2C%20passed%20three%20bills%20in%20a%20span%20of%20less%20than%2030%20minutes%20as%20opposition%20members%20continued%20to%20raise%20slogans%20demanding%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20Manipur%2C%20calling%20the%20swift%20passage%20of%20the%20bills%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20House%20was%20initially%20adjourned%20within%20minutes%20of%20the%20day%20commencing.%20It%20reconvened%20at%20noon%2C%20and%20by%2012.35%20pm%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20introduced%20and%20passed%20three%20bills.%20The%20session%20was%20then%20adjourned%20for%20the%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20bills%20that%20were%20introduced%20and%20passed%20are%20The%20National%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery%20Commission%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20The%20National%20Dental%20Commission%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20and%20The%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20continues%20demand%20for%20PM%E2%80%99s%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20House%20opened%20this%20morning%2C%20opposition%20MPs%20raised%20slogans%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20put%20forth%20the%20argument%20that%20considering%20the%20notice%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-congress-no-confidence-modi-speaker%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno-confidence%20motion%20had%20already%20been%20accepted%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20no%20other%20business%20should%20be%20conducted%20till%20the%20motion%20is%20discussed%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeader%20of%20Congress%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%20that%20in%20May%201978%2C%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20moved%2C%20a%20discussion%20was%20held%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20same%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20in%20response%20said%20that%20he%20will%20give%20a%20date%20for%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20and%20asked%20the%20opposition%20members%20to%20allow%20the%20Question%20Hour%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rules%20state%20that%20we%20have%2010%20days%E2%80%99%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Minister%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%2C%20Pralhad%20Joshi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20you%20(Speaker)%20decide%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20discussion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirla%20then%20adjourned%20the%20session%20till%20noon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20house%20reconvened%20at%20noon%2C%20Rajendra%20Agarwal%20took%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair%20and%20began%20the%20session%E2%80%99s%20proceedings%20as%20opposition%20members%20continued%20to%20raise%20slogans%20saying%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cpradhan%20mantri%20jawab%20do%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(p%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erime%20minister%2C%20answer)%2C%E2%80%9D%20holding%20banners%20that%20read%20%E2%80%9CSave%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.07%20pm%2C%20the%20Minister%20for%20Education%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20introduced%20The%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Management%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20This%20Bill%20was%20not%20passed%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20next%20week%20for%20consideration%20and%20passing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.09%20pm%2C%20The%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%20and%20passed%20as%20opposition%20members%20were%20seen%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair%20holding%20banners%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20amends%20the%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Act%2C%201957.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fthe-mines-and-minerals-development-and-regulation-amendment-bill-2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20summary%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20the%20earlier%20Act%20prohibited%20pitting%2C%20trenching%2C%20drilling%2C%20and%20sub-surface%20excavation%20as%20part%20of%20reconnaissance%20%E2%80%93%20the%20new%20Bill%20allows%20these%20prohibited%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20introduces%20an%20exploration%20licence%2C%20which%20will%20authorise%20either%20reconnaissance%20or%20prospecting%2C%20or%20both%20activities%20for%20specified%20minerals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exploration%20licence%20will%20be%20issued%20for%2029%20minerals%20specified%20in%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule.%20These%20include%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20copper%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20lead%2C%20potash%2C%20and%20rock%20phosphate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exploration%20licence%20will%20be%20granted%20by%20the%20state%20government%20through%20competitive%20bidding%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20prescribe%20details%20such%20as%20manner%20of%20auction%2C%20terms%20and%20conditions%2C%20and%20bidding%20parameters%20for%20exploration%20licence%20through%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20under%20the%20earlier%20Act%20auction%20of%20concessions%20was%20undertaken%20by%20the%20state%20governments%2C%20except%20in%20certain%20specified%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20the%20amended%20Bill%20adds%20that%20auction%20for%20composite%20licence%20and%20mining%20lease%20for%20specified%20critical%20and%20strategic%20minerals%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20central%20government.%C2%A0%20These%20minerals%20include%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20phosphate%2C%20potash%2C%20tin%2C%20phosphate%2C%20and%20potash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20exploration%20licence%20would%20facilitate%2C%20encourage%20and%20incentivize%20private%20sector%20participation%20in%20all%20spheres%20of%20mineral%20exploration%20for%20critical%20and%20deep-seated%20minerals%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FMines%2520and%2520Minerals%2520(Development%2520and%2520Regulation)%2520Amendment%2520Bill%2C%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20coals%20and%20mines%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20(who%20also%20has%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20portfolio)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20N.K.%20Premachandran%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%20had%20said%20that%20it%20is%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20federalism%20and%20will%20benefit%20multinational%20corporations%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcoal%2Fmines-and-minerals-development-and-regulation-amendment-bill-2023-introduced-in-lok-sabha%2F102139537%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20two%20MPs%20spoke%20during%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Bill%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Singh%20BJP%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20amendment%20will%20allow%20India%20to%20become%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ea%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Etmarnirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20word%20for%20%E2%80%98self%20reliant%E2%80%99%20and%20often%20a%20catchphrase%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20%E2%80%93%20and%20allow%20India%20to%20strengthen%20its%20position%20in%20the%20global%20market%20and%20remove%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20to%20gain%20licences%20and%20help%20mining%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MP%20M%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20was%20then%20asked%20to%20speak%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20seen%20raising%20copies%20of%20the%20constitution%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.15%20pm%2C%20minister%20Joshi%20gave%20his%20closing%20statement%2C%20calling%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%9Crevolutionary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20visible%20change%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%20because%20of%20our%20policies%20and%20we%20have%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20of%20the%20world%20under%20Modi.%20With%20a%20clear%20vision%20and%20mind%20we%20are%20bringing%20changes%20that%20will%20benefit%20the%20nation%20not%20dynasties.%20Their%20(opposition)%20MP%20has%20even%20been%20jailed%20for%20coal%20allocation%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20passed%2C%20it%20will%20boost%20exploration%20for%20critical%2Fdeep%20seated%20minerals%20helping%20indigenous%20technologies%20in%20space%20industry%2C%20electronics%2C%20energy%20sector%20and%20EVs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMy%20reply%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20The%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20passed%2C%20it%20will%20boost%20exploration%20for%20critical%2Fdeep%20seated%20minerals%20helping%20indigenous%20technologies%20in%20space%20industry%2C%20electro