0the%20country's%20development%20and%20have%20made%20it%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20rapidly%20eradicated%20extreme%20poverty%20and%20seen%20a%20fast%20rise%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bneo-middle%20class%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20India%20understands%20its%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20responsibility%26quot%3B%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20wide%20roadmap%20together%20with%20our%20friendly%20countries.%20We%20are%20taking%20special%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%20semiconductor%20ecosystem%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20country%20recently%20approved%20the%20'National%20Quantum%20Mission'%20and%20is%20going%20to%20introduce%20the%20Nation%20Research%20Foundation%20Bill%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Quantum%20Mission%20aims%20to%20seed%2C%20nurture%20and%20scale%20up%20scientific%20and%20industrial%20research%20and%20development%20and%20create%20a%20vibrant%20and%20innovative%20ecosystem%20in%20quantum%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20semiconductor%20ecosystem%2C%20we%20are%20changing%20the%20engineering%20curriculum.%20India%20has%20identified%20more%20than%20300%20big%20colleges%20where%20courses%20will%20be%20offered%20on%20semiconductors.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20we%20will%20have%20more%20than%201%20lakh%20design%20engineers.%20India's%20continuously%20growing%20startup%20ecosystem%20will%20also%20provide%20strength%20to%20the%20semiconductor%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20that%20electricity%20is%20required%20for%20this%20sector%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20country's%20installed%20solar%20power%20capacity%20has%20multiplied%2020%20times%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20set%20a%20target%20for%20500%20gigawatts%20of%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade%20and%20has%20taken%20