%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20having%20the%20protagonist%20in%20this%20movie%20declare%20that%20%E2%80%98Every%20relationship%20goes%20through%20their%20Auschwitz%E2%80%99%2C%20Nitesh%20Tiwari%20%5Bthe%20director%5D%2C%20trivialises%20and%20demeans%20the%20memory%20of%20six%20million%20murdered%20Jews%20and%20millions%20of%20others%20who%20suffered%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20regime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20filmmaker%E2%80%99s%20goal%20was%20to%20gain%20PR%20%5Bpublicity%5D%20for%20their%20movie%20by%20reportedly%20filming%20a%20fantasy%20sequence%20at%20the%20Nazi%20death%20camp%2C%20he%20has%20succeeded%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20asked%20Amazon%20Prime%20to%20remove%20the%20film%20from%20its%20platform%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20cast%20and%20director%20have%20called%20the%20criticism%20against%20the%20film%20unwarranted%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20trailer%2C%20Jahnvi%20Kapoor%E2%80%99s%20character%2C%20Nisha%2C%20says%20to%20her%20husband%20Ajay%2C%20played%20by%20Varun%20Dhawan%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20all%20a%20little%20bit%20like%20Hitler%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20not%20happy%20with%20what%20we%20have.%20And%20we%20want%20what%20others%20have.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20scene%20in%20the%20film%2C%20she%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20relationship%20goes%20through%20their%20Auschwitz.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Auschwitz%20concentration%20camp%20was%20one%20of%20many%20locations%20where%20Adolf%20Hilter%E2%80%99s%20Nazi%20regime%20brought%20Jews%20and%20others%20from%20all%20over%20Europe%20to%20be%20starved%2C%20humiliated%2C%20terrorised%2C%20and%20murdered%20in%20gas%20chambers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20scenes%20are%20intended%20to%20draw%20a%20parallel%20between%20the%20protagonists%E2%80%99%20love%20story%20and%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20also%20includes%20a%20fantasy%20scene%20inside%20a%20gas%20chamber%20and%20uses%20Hitler%20and%20the%20Auschwitz%20death%20camp%20as%20metaphors.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690550936000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28185246%2Fimage-1178.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fisraeli-embassy-jewish-rights-group-criticise-bawaal-maker-for-trivialising-holocaust%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'There%20was%20a%20poor%20choice%20in%20the%20utilisation%20of%20some%20terminology%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20and%20though%20we%20assume%20no%20malice%20was%20intended%2C%20we%20urge%20everyone%20who%20may%20not%20be%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20to%20educate%20themselves%20about%20it%2C'%20said%20the%20embassy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fisraeli-embassy-jewish-rights-group-criticise-bawaal-maker-for-trivialising-holocaust%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Courts%20Not%20A%20Panacea%20For%20All%20Things%20Wrong%20In%20Country%5C%22%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20petition%20filed%20in%202019%20by%20a%20two-year-old%20seeking%20a%20CBI%20or%20an%20SIT%20investigation%20into%20complaints%20of%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwell-organised%26quot%3B%20kidney%20transplant%20scam%20involving%20corporate%20hospitals%20in%20several%20states%2C%20saying%20courts%20cannot%20be%20%26quot%3Bpanacea%26quot%3B%20for%20all%20things%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20S%20K%20Kaul%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20said%20the%20court%20cannot%20be%20like%20an%20all-encompassing%20system%20trying%20to%20do%20everything.%20It%20said%20these%20are%20administrative%20issues%20for%20the%20police%20and%20the%20executive%20mechanism%20to%20deal%20with.%20In%20August%202019%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20others%20on%20the%20plea%20of%20a%2023-month-old%20infant%20who%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20through%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20was%20suffering%20from%20West%20syndrome%2C%20a%20condition%20in%20which%20children%20have%20seizures%20and%20cognitive%20and%20developmental%20impairment.%20It%20had%20rendered%20him%20mentally%20disabled%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20birth%20at%20a%20private%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20on%20Friday%2C%20advocate%20Sachin%20Jain%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20about%20five%20recent%20instances%20of%20alleged%20kidney%20racket%20in%202023%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20January%202013%20report%20of%20the%20Justice%20(retd)%20J%20S%20Verma%20committee%2C%20which%20had%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20children%20being%20driven%20into%20forced%20labour%2C%20sex%20abuse%20and%20made%20victims%20of%20illegal%20human%20organ%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20inclined%20to%20entertain%20the%20petition%20any%20further%20but%20call%20upon%20the%20respondents%20(Centre%20and%20others)%20to%20look%20into%20the%20issue%20flagged%20by%20the%20petitioner%20and%20take%20necessary%20action%2C%20especially%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Justice%20J%20S%20Verma%20committee%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20bench%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20running%20mechanism%20for%20everything%2C%20every%20department%2C%20every%20system%3F%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said%20such%20scams%20have%20inter-state%20and%20international%20connections%2C%20and%20a%20central%20agency%20should%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20probing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20administrative%20issues.%20There%20is%20a%20police%20mechanism.%20There%20is%20an%20executive%20mechanism%20to%20handle%20it.%20We%20can't%20take%20over%20the%20burden%20of%20everything%20and%20start%20doing%20it%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20if%20in%20a%20particular%20incident%20things%20are%20not%20working%2C%20the%20court%20examines%20it%20and%20passes%20judicial%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(court)%20is%20not%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20things%20which%20may%20be%20wrong%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202019%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20others%20including%20the%20states%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Delhi%20on%20the%20plea%20which%20said%20the%20probe%20should%20be%20monitored%20by%20a%20committee%20comprising%20one%20or%20more%20former%20judges%20or%20senior%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20had%20also%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20three%20states%20to%20undertake%20a%20campaign%20to%20create%20awareness%20among%20the%20underprivileged%20sections%20about%20the%20menace%20of%20organ%20trade%20and%20to%20acquaint%20them%20with%20their%20rights%20and%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%2C%20which%20mentioned%20media%20reports%20about%20kidney%20trafficking%2C%20had%20claimed%20a%20large%20number%20of%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20citizens%20were%20being%20frequently%20%26quot%3Bcoerced%2C%20forced%20and%20compelled%26quot%3B%20to%20sell%20their%20kidneys%2C%20and%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20preventive%20measures%20to%20stop%20this%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20alleged%20organ%20trafficking%20involved%20some%20medical%20practitioners%2C%20who%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20sheep%26quot%3B