%20Month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20cinema%2C%20a%20powerful%20tool%20to%20map%20the%20real%20world%2C%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20encouraging%20this%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20acceptance%20of%20diversity.%20It%20bears%20the%20responsibility%20of%20disseminating%20awareness%20and%20education%20to%20nurture%20a%20world%20that%20is%20sensitive%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20sees%20them%20as%20people%20first%20over%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20where%20does%20cinema%20stand%20in%20this%20respect%20today%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98No%20visible%20boundaries%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20first%2C%20what%20is%20Disability%20Pride%20month%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22disability%20pride%20flag%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdisability-pride-flag-1690540782-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325551%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20observed%20in%201990%2C%20Disability%20Pride%20Month%20commemorates%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Americans%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20on%20July%2026%2C%20