0created%20technical%20issues%20for%20implementing%20all-out%20army%20operations%20as%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690548240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F5rfn5rvg_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_05_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-10-challenges-in-manipur-that-are-fuelling-the-violence-4248899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20three%20months%20after%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20between%20the%20Kuki%20tribal%20group%20and%20the%20ethnic%20majority%20Meiteis%20over%20sharing%20economic%20benefits%20and%20quotas%20given%20to%20the%20tribes%2C%20there%20are%20little%20signs%20of%20the%20conflict%20coming%20to%20an%20end.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-10-challenges-in-manipur-that-are-fuelling-the-violence-4248899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-10-challenges-in-manipur-that-are-fuelling-the-violence-4248899%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-10-challenges-in-manipur-that-are-fuelling-the-violence-4248899%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%E2%80%99m%20in%20Favour%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20but%20What%20I%20Want%20Is%20Total%20Gender%20Equality'%3A%20Javed%20Akhtar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28175309%2Fimage-1177.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20well-known%20poet%2C%20lyricist%2C%20and%20scriptwriter%2C%20Javed%20Akhtar%2C%20has%20categorically%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20desirable%20and%20necessary.%20He%20added%20that%20for%20him%2C%20personally%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20ensure%20complete%20and%20comprehensive%20gender%20equality%2C%20without%20any%20discrimination%20whatsoever%20for%20either%20the%20girl%20child%20or%20the%20adult%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20cannot%20delay%20giving%20itself%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20time%20is%20not%20right%2C%20said%20Akhtar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20will%20never%20be%20right%20because%20there%20will%20always%20be%20people%20opposed%20to%20it.%20While%20efforts%20must%20be%20made%20to%20convince%20everyone%2C%20we%20cannot%20give%20a%20veto%20to%20extremists%20of%20any%20community%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2040-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Akhtar%20said%20that%20the%20most%20important%20first%20step%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20to%20place%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Without%20such%20a%20draft%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20all%20conversation%20and%20debate%20is%20meaningless.%20This%20draft%2C%20he%20said%2C%20must%20be%20created%20by%20experts%20and%20not%20by%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20suggestions%20from%20citizens%2C%20communities%2C%20or%20institutions%20should%20come%20after%20such%20a%20draft%20is%20made%20available%2C%20not%20before.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20this%20is%20happening%20the%20wrong%20way%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhtar%20further%20said%20that%20while%20it%E2%80%99s%20understandable%20that%20tribals%20like%20the%20Santhals%2C%20the%20Sentinelese%2C%20the%20Jarawas%2C%20or%20those%20in%20Bastar%2C%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20excluded%2C%20because%20we%20need%20to%20be%20sensitive%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20effectively%20live%20in%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%20time%20zones%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20states%20of%20the%20North%20East%2C%20which%20are%20also%20considered%20%5Ba%20home%20to%20the%5D%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20must%20not%20be%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20would%20mean%20the%20end%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Hindu%20Undivided%20Family%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20end%20of%20restrictions%20on%20marriages%20within%20a%20%3Cem%3Egotra%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20judgments%20on%20inter-caste%20marriages%20by%20khap%20panchayats.%20All%20of%20this%20would%20have%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20about%20the%20intention%20behind%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20he%20said%20this%20is%20not%20something%20that%20concerns%20or%20matters%20to%20him.%20As%20he%20put%20it%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20if%20someone%20with%20the%20wrong%20intentions%20does%20the%20right%20thing.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20right%20thing%20is%20being%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20said%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20being%20raised%20as%20a%20dog%20whistle%20to%20target%20the%20Muslim%20community%20or%20as%20an%20election%20issue%20that%20might%20improve%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20himself%20personally%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20personally%20lived%20his%20life%20as%20if%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20applies%20to%20him.%20He%20said%20as%20a%20Muslim%2C%20he%20is%20only%20required%20to%20pay%20alimony%20to%20his%20first%20wife%20for%20four%20months%20but%20he%20has%20consciously%20and%20deliberately%20chosen%20to%20pay%20it%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20wanted%20it.%20He%20also%20said%20in%20terms%20of%20inheritance%20and%20his%20treatment%20of%20them%2C%20he%20has%20treated%20his%20son%20and%20daughter%20exactly%20equally%20and%20ensured%20that%20they%20will%20each%20get%20a%2050%25%20share%20of%20what%20he%20leaves%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20for%20him%2C%20the%20most%20important%20issue%20is%20gender%20equality%20and%20absolutely%20no%20discrimination%20against%20women.%20He%20says%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20this%20is%20delivered%20through%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20or%20in%20some%20other%20way%2C%20but%20this%20remains%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJqZsQRSF8p4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690547178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28175309%2Fimage-1177.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Ffavour-of-uniform-civil-code-want-total-gender-equality-javed-akhtar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akhtar%20said%20that%20the%20most%20important%20first%20step%20for%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20to%20place%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Without%20such%20a%20draft%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20all%20conversation%20and%20debate%20is%20meaningless.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Ffavour-of-uniform-civil-code-want-total-gender-equality-javed-akhtar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Binny%2C%20Laxman%20to%20speak%20to%20Harmanpreet%20about%20her%20outburst'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690546205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102205949%2Cimgsize-27118.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Froger-binny-vvs-laxman-to-speak-to-harmanpreet-kaur-about-her-outburst-jay-shah%2Farticleshow%2F102205792.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BCCI%20will%20not%20appeal%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur's%20two-match%20ban%2C%20as%20appeal%20time%20is%20over.%20BCCI%20president%20Roger%20Binny%20and%20NCA%20head%20VVS%20Laxman%20will%20discuss%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20India%20skipper.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Froger-binny-vvs-laxman-to-speak-to-harmanpreet-kaur-about-her-outburst-jay-shah%2Farticleshow%2F102205792.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2220-member%20INDIA%20delegation%20to%20visit%20Manipur%20tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690546191000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-102206004%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-1315799%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwill-find-out-the-truth-20-member-india-delegation-to-visit-manipur-on-july-29-30%2Farticleshow%2F102205553.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20delegation%20of%2020%20MPs%20from%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%20will%20visit%20Manipur%20on%20July%2029-30%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20which%20has%20been%20engulfed%20in%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203.%20The%20delegation%20will%20visit%20both%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20hill%20regions%20of%20the%20state%20and%20meet%20different%20communities%20there.%20They%20will%20also%20visit%20some%20relief%20camps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwill-find-out-the-truth-20-member-india-delegation-to-visit-manipur-on-july-29-30%2Farticleshow%2F102205553.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20No-Trust%20Vote%20Plays%20In%20PM%20Modi's%20Favour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20a%20prophetic%20statement%20in%20parliament%3A%20%26quot%3BOnce%20again%20I%20want%20to%20give%20my%20best%20wishes%20to%20you%2C%20may%20you%20work%20harder%20that%20you%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20again%20in%202023.%26quot%3B%20The%20treasury%20benches%20burst%20into%20loud%20cheers%20and%20laughter.%20The%20video%20clip%20has%20now%20gone%20viral%20on%20all%20media%20platforms%2C%20social%20and%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20wonders%20why%20on%2026%20July%202023%2C%20the%20newly%20formed%2026-party%20opposition%20grouping%2C%20INDIA%2C%20was%20so%20hell%20bent%20to%20prove%20Modi's%20prophesy%20right%20by%20moving%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%2026%20July%20is%20the%20date%20when%20the%20nation%2C%20for%20two-and-a-half%20decades%2C%20celebrates%20the%20day%20as%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20brute%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20motion%20is%20known.%20So%2C%20why%20is%20one%20looking%20forward%20to%20it%20with%20excitement%20and%20anticipation%3F%20The%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20debate%20and%20all%20hype%20around%20it%2C%20will%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20be%20centred%20around%20one%20question%20--%20who%20gains%20and%20who%20loses%20in%20setting%20the%20right%20narrative%2C%20setting%20the%20agenda%2C%20giving%20talking%20points%20and%20galvanising%20its%20rank%20and%20file%20to%20take%20on%20the%20rival%20political%20formation%20for%20April-May%202024%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20grouping%20INDIA%20gives%20an%20unconvincing%20argument%20for%20moving%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20-%20to%20force%20PM%20Modi%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur.%20Over%2050%20thinking%20heads%20of%20the%2026-party%20opposition%20grouping%20must%20have%20gone%20into%20detail%20over%20the%20issue%20before%2C%20making%20the%20intent%20known%20and%20moving%20the%20motion.%20In%20their%20wisdom%2C%20they%20must%20have%20thought%20it%20to%20be%20a%20wonderful%20idea%20to%20bring%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20to%20their%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20actually%20doing%20a%20huge%20favour%20to%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20by%20pushing%20this%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government.%20It%20may%20just%20be%20committing%20a%20self-goal%20or%20as%20the%20Hindi%20idiom%20goes%2C%20'%3Cem%3EAa%20bail%20mujhe%20maar%3C%2Fem%3E'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20seriously%20concerned%20over%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20is%20moving%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20to%20force%20PM%20Modi%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20same%20issue.%20The%20question%20is%20-%20hasn't%20the%20chair%20of%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20agreed%20or%20even%20given%20the%20ruling%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%3F%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20opposition%20grouping%20INDIA%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue.%20But%20the%20contention%20is%2C%20under%20what%20rule%3F%20Does%20it%20really%20matter%20to%20people%20at%20large%2C%20more%20so%20to%20people%20of%20Manipur%20under%20which%20rule%20the%20issue%20is%20taken%20up%20in%20Parliament%3F%20For%20people%2C%20rules%2C%20A%20or%20B%20for%20a%20discussion%20is%20far%20too%20abstract%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20out%20there%20is%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20a%20one-line%20motion%20which%20does%20not%20mention%20any%20specific%20issue.%20So%20almost%20anything%20under%20the%20sun%20can%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20Speaker%20concerned%20to%20take%20on%20its%20rival%2C%20ruling%20and%20opposition%20parties.%20It%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20Manipur.%20A%20whole%20lot%20of%20other%20issues%20will%20come%20into%20play%20from%20both%20sides.%20Manipur%20will%20only%20be%20the%20one%20among%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20occasion%20to%20see%20who%20exposes%20whom.%20The%20INDIA%20formation%20surely%20thinks%20that%20it%20will%20expose%20the%20government%20and%20PM%20Modi%20in%20particular.%20But%20should%20it%20be%20reminded%20of%20the%202018%20no-confidence%20motion%20when%20Modi%20tore%20them%20apart%20in%20his%20concluding%20speech.%20In%20the%20following%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20further%20strengthened%20its%20position%2C%20winning%20303%20seats%20on%20its%20own%20and%20two-thirds%20with%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20oratorical%20skills%20are%20beyond%20doubt.%20He%20will%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20about%20Manipur%2C%20its%20historicity%2C%20the%20way%20successive%20Congress%20governments%20handled%20it%2C%20the%20present%20conflict%20situation%20there%2C%20and%20the%20viral%20video%20(about%20which%20he%20has%20already%20spoken).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20will%20also%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20about%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20How%20similar%20crimes%20in%20these%20states%20were%20brushed%20under%20the%20carpet%20by%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%2C%20Left-Liberal%20groups%20and%20its%20echo%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20while%20inaugurating%20the%20newly-built%20architectural%20marvel%2C%20Bharat%20Mandapam%2C%20International%20Exhibition%20cum%20Convention%20Centre%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20Modi%20gave%20an%20indication%20on%20how%20his%20speech%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20could%20go%20-%20he%20spoke%20about%20his%20third%20term%20in%20government%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20guarantee%26quot%3B%20-%20in%20his%20next%20term%2C%20how%20India%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20also%20took%20on%20his%20rivals%20and%20critics%20for%20trying%20to%20stall%20the%20project%20through%20various%20means%20including%20petitioning%20the%20judiciary%20on%20one%20pretext%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20occasion%20will%20also%20give%20Modi%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20opposition%20from%20a%20public%20platform%20over%20the%20INDIA%20name%20and%20its%20inner%20contradictions.%20He%20could%20even%20highlight%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20UPA%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20NDA%20celebrating%2025%20years%20of%20its%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20bending%20backward%20to%20accommodate%20the%20hard%20push%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20That%20becomes%20even%20more%20interesting%20in%20view%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20a%20straight%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%20fight%20in%20190%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20-%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%2092%20per%20cent%20-%20won%20175%20and%20the%20Congress%20could%20manage%20only%2015%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20speakers%20may%20highlight%20this%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20INDIA%20moved%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20on%20July%2026%2C%20which%20the%20nation%20celebrates%20as%20Kargil%20Victory%20Day.%20The%20Congress%20is%20inadvertently%20providing%20the%20BJP%20further%20ammo%20by%20clubbing%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20presence%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20with%20the%20so-called%20Tukde%20Tukde%20Gang%2C%20Khoon%20Ki%20Dalali.%20His%20recent%20statements%20abroad%20that%20India%20is%20not%20a%20nation%20and%20asking%20the%20US%20and%20Western%20nations%20to%20intervene%20in%20India%20against%20Modi%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20democracy%26quot%3B%2C%20did%20him%20no%20favours.%20He%20called%20ally%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20secular%20party%26quot%3B.%20It%20was%20reminiscent%20of%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20seeking%20Pakistan's%20intervention%20to%20remove%20Modi.%20The%20BJP%20may%20like%20to%20make%20a%20further%20dent%20in%20the%20already%20bruised%20nationalist%20credentials%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20grouping%20leaders%20are%20doing%20no%20favour%20to%20themselves%20by%20making%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20often%20wear%20'%3Cem%3Ekala%20kapda%3C%2Fem%3E'%20or%20black%20clothes%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20their%20protest%20in%20Parliament.%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Union%20Commerce%20Minister%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20Piyush%20Goyal%20was%20very%20sarcastic%20about%20that%2C%20equating%20their%20black%20dress%20with%20their%20dark%20future%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20when%20on%20August%205%2C%20the%20Congress%20staged%20a%20'%3Cem%3Ekala%20kapda%3C%2Fem%3E'%20protest%20against%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20turned%20the%20tables%20on%20them%2C%20questioning%20-%20%26quot%3BWhy%20choose%20the%20day%20when%20PM%20Modi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20missed%20during%20the%20no-confidence%20debate.%20He%20has%20brought%20in%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20aggression%20and%20colour%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20past.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20disqualified%20and%20as%20of%20now%20he%20can't%20contest%20either%202024%20or%202029%20elections%2C%20for%20many%20people%2C%20he%20remains%20to%20be%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20of%20the%20Opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20may%20not%20be%20a%20great%20orator%20but%20his%20presence%20and%20speech%20draws%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20attention%20from%20the%20people%20and%20from%20the%20media.%20His%20absence%20may%20not%20be%20a%20happy%20situation%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20some%20others%20in%20the%20opposition%20benches%20may%20be%20happy%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20make%20their%20presence%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690545720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7jl3gn1g_mallikarjun-kharge-with-other-leaders-in-parliament-pti-650_650x400_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-no-trust-vote-plays-in-pm-modis-favour-4248719%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20wonders%20why%20on%2026%20July%202023%2C%20the%20newly%20formed%2026-party%20opposition%20grouping%2C%20INDIA%2C%20was%20so%20hell%20bent%20to%20prove%20Modi's%20prophesy%20right%20by%20moving%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20his%20government%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-no-trust-vote-plays-in-pm-modis-favour-4248719%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-no-trust-vote-plays-in-pm-modis-favour-4248719%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-no-trust-vote-plays-in-pm-modis-favour-4248719%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unicorns%20Have%20Lost%20the%20Numbers%20Game%20%E2%80%93%20It%E2%80%99s%20Time%20For%20Proficorns%20to%20Take%20the%20Stage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28172130%2Fimage-1176.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2F70-of-last-years-taxpayers-now-below%5C%22%3Ewas%20first%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20t%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer