2content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Assam%20unit%20president%20Bhupen%20Borah%20on%20Friday%20apologised%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-triple-murder-himanta-biswa-sarma-bhupen-kumar-bora-arrest-warning-for-assam-congress-chief-over-lord-krishna-love-jihad-parallel-4247398%5C%22%3Edrawing%20a%20parallel%20between%20'love%20jihad'%20and%20Lord%20Krishna's%20relationship%20with%20Rukmini%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20commenting%20on%20the%20triple%20murder%20case%20in%20Golaghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20man%20killed%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20parents%20over%20some%20family%20issues%2C%20and%20later%20surrendered%20before%20the%20police%20in%20Golaghat%20district.%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20'love%20jihad'%20as%20the%20husband%20was%20Muslim%20and%20the%20wife%20a%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20it%2C%20Mr%20Borah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20is%20fair%20in%20love%20and%20war.%20There%20are%20many%20stories%20in%20our%20ancient%20texts%2C%20including%20Krishna%20eloping%20with%20Rukmini%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20not%20harp%20about%20marriages%20between%20people%20of%20different%20religions%20and%20communities%20in%20today's%20age.%26quot%3B%20As%20the%20comment%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20Mr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20warned%20that%20he%20may%20be%20arrested%20if%20a%20police%20case%20is%20filed%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20apologised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20dream%20last%20night%2C%20my%20grandfather%20told%20me%20that%20the%20statement%20was%20wrong%2C%20and%20it%20has%20hurt%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%2C%20therefore%2C%20decided%20to%20offer%20an%20earthen%20lamp%20and%20betel%20leaf%20and%20areca%20nut%20at%20a%20'namghar'%20(Vaishnavite%20prayer%20hall)%20and%20seek%20forgiveness%20from%20the%20lord.%20I%20will%20do%20this%20not%20because%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20as%20the%20people%20and%20the%20Sattradhikars%20(Vaishnav%20spiritual%20heads)%20have%20been%20hurt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20BJP's%20demand%20that%20he%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20'namghars'%2C%20Mr%20Borah%20said%20the%20chief%20minister%20should%20rather%20%26quot%3Bask%20the%20police%20to%20kill%20me%20in%20an%20encounter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20ready%20to%20sacrifice%20my%20life%2C%20and%20my%20family%20will%20not%20file%20any%20case%2C%20but%20I%20should%20not%20be%20stopped%20from%20going%20to%20the%20prayer%20hall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP's%20youth%20wing%20BJYM%20filed%20police%20complaints%20in%20all%20the%20districts%20of%20the%20state%20against%20Mr%20Borah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuwahati%20city%20BYJM%20president%20Nihar%20Ranjan%20Sharma%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20Pan%20Bazaar%20police%20station%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20has%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActually%2C%20he%20has%20made%20the%20statement%20as%20he%20is%20scared%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20party%2C%20which%20is%20absolutely%20dark.%20We%20hope%20God%20gives%20him%20good%20sense%2C%20and%20he%20changes%20for%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20had%20on%20Thursday%20criticised%20Mr%20Borah's%20remarks%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20take%20the%20step%20of%20arresting%20people%20but%20if%20Lord%20Krishna%20is%20dragged%20into%20controversy%2C%20several%20'sanatani'%20people%20will%20file%20cases%20in%20police%20stations%20and%20then%20how%20will%20I%20stop%20the%20police%20from%20taking%20action%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20files%20a%20case%20against%20a%20person%20for%20making%20such%20comments%2C%20he%20will%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Mr%20Borah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Love%20jihad'%20is%20a%20situation%20when%20a%20girl%20is%20forced%20to%20marry%20by%20changing%20her%20religion%20and%20Krishna%20did%20not%20force%20Rukmini%20to%20change%20her%20religion%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20'love%20jihad'%20is%20used%20by%20right-wing%20groups%20to%20allege%20a%20ploy%20by%20Muslim%20men%20to%20lure%20Hindu%20women%20into%20religious%20conversion%20through%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690543680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F8lktqh3_bhupen-borah-twitter_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-congress-president-apologises-for-love-jihad-lord-krishna-parallel-4248554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress's%20Assam%20unit%20president%20Bhupen%20Bora%20on%20Friday%20apologised%20for%20drawing%20a%20parallel%20between%20'love%20jihad'%20and%20Lord%20Krishna's%20relationship%20with%20Rukmini%20while%20commenting%20on%20the%20triple%20murder%20case%20in%20Golaghat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-congress-president-apologises-for-love-jihad-lord-krishna-parallel-4248554%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-congress-president-apologises-for-love-jihad-lord-krishna-parallel-4248554%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-congress-president-apologises-for-love-jihad-lord-krishna-parallel-4248554%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26K%20Admin%20Transfers%20Senior%20Official%20After%20He%20Flagged%20Hotel%20Construction%20Violations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214048%2FHotel-2-huts.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20administration%20shunted%20out%20a%20senior%20officer%20for%20allegedly%20flagging%20violations%20by%20an%20under-construction%20hotel%20in%20a%20Pahalgam%20health%20resort%20in%20south%20Kashmir%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%2C%20which%20comprises%20three%20huts%20and%20includes%20a%20staff%20quarter%2C%20is%20coming%20up%20in%20Athnadan%20village%2C%20located%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20eco-fragile%20Pahalgam%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20documents%2C%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%20started%20in%20April%20this%20year%20and%20the%20builder%20was%20found%20by%20officials%20to%20be%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20permission%20granted%20by%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violation%20was%20highlighted%20by%20the%20chief%20executive%20officer%20(CEO)%20of%20the%20Pahalgam%20Development%20Authority%20(PDA)%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%20of%20Anantnag%2C%20seeking%20his%20permission%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20violation%20by%20demolishing%20the%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDA%20is%20the%20nodal%20authority%20which%20manages%20the%20health%20resort%20and%20also%20grants%20permission%20for%20new%20constructions%20after%20getting%20them%20approved%20by%20the%20Building%20Operation%20Controlling%20Authority%20(BOCA)%20of%20the%20PDA%2C%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20against%20the%20hotelier%2C%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%20amended%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20building%20permission%2C%20and%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20was%20shunted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20sent%20a%20detailed%20questionnaire%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%2C%20seeking%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20committed%20by%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20documents%20and%20sources%2C%20permission%20for%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20construction%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20in%20its%2013th%20meeting%20on%20October%206%20and%20October%2025%20last%20year.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20permission%20letter%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20owner%20was%20directed%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20first%20hut%20in%20first%20stage%20of%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%5Bthe%5D%20completion%20of%20one%20hut%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20second%20%5Bhut%5D%20shall%20be%20started%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20states%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cregeneration%20of%20the%20natural%20landscape%E2%80%9D%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20environment%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Lidder%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27214742%2FKey-tributary-of-Lidder-Low.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20under-construction%20hotel%20is%20situated%20barely%20100%20metres%20from%20one%20of%20the%20key%20tributaries%20of%20the%20Lidder%20river%20in%20Pahalgam.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20hotel%20started%20in%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20PDA%20CEO%2C%20a%20local%20activist%20named%20Mudasir%20Ahmed%20alleged%20that%20the%20owner%20had%20violated%20the%20terms%20of%20permission.%20The%20letter%20states%20that%20the%20hotel%20owner%20had%20used%20%E2%80%9Cnon-permissible%20machinery%20to%20change%20the%20topography%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20eco-fragile%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20locals%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20PDA%2C%20seeking%20verification%20of%20the%20revenue%20records%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20hotel%20may%20be%20coming%20up%20on%20a%20flood%20water%20channel%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20government%20but%20under%20the%20care%20of%20locals%2C%20and%20not%20proprietary%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20case%20under%20observance%20%5Bsic%5D%20needs%20official%20probe%20to%20know%20the%20reality%20currently%20dancing%20behind%20the%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20has%20been%20marked%20to%20the%20Kashmir%20divisional%20commissioner%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20served%20as%20a%20discharge%20canal%20for%20cloudbursts%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Pahalgam%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20wishing%20anonymity%20said%2C%20while%20demanding%C2%A0%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20fudging%20of%20revenue%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20administration%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20this%20claim%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20hotel%20was%20coming%20up%20on%20proprietary%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20not%20immediately%20verify%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20a%20PDA%20team%20visited%20the%20site%20in%20May%20and%20found%20that%20the%20hotel%20was%20being%20built%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20terms%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20BOCA.%20Following%20the%20visit%2C%20the%20then-CEO%2C%20Syed%20Sajad%20Qadri%2C%20a%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20officer%2C%20flagged%20the%20violations%20to%20the%20Anantnag%20DC%2C%20Syeed%20Fakhrudin%20Hamid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20property%20owner%20on%20May%2018%2C%20the%20assistant%20executive%20engineer%20of%20the%20PDA%20stated%20that%20during%20the%20site%20inspection%2C%20it%20was%20noted%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20you%20have%20violated%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20the%20permission%20%E2%80%A6%20by%20starting%20construction%20work%20of%20all%20three%20huts%20altogether%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20%5Ba%5D%20column-type%20structure%20instead%20of%20%5Ba%5D%20load-bearing%20structure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDA%20notice%20warned%20the%20hotel%20owner%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20the%20construction%20work%20immediately%20and%20rectify%20the%20deviation%20within%20two%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20of%20failure%20the%20same%20shall%20be%20demolished%20by%20the%20Pahalgam%20Development%20Authority%20at%20your%20risk%20and%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PDA%20notice%2C%20which%20was%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27215812%2FHotel-from-far.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20material%20used%20by%20the%20hotelier%20has%20been%20dumped%20on%20the%20pristine%20meadows%2C%20damaging%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20area.%20Photo%3A%20Jehangir%20Ali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%20the%20PDA%20CEO%20wrote%20to%20Anantnag%20DC%20Fakhrudin%20Hamid%20seeking%20permission%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20buildings%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20the%20applicant%20fails%20to%20follow%20the%20conditions%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20permission%20letter.%E2%80%9D%20The%20letter%20came%20after%20an%20%E2%80%9Cemergency%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20was%20called%20by%20the%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20states%20that%20the%20building%20plan%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20which%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20(the%20only%20authority%20empowered%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20to%20building%20plans)%2C%20was%20allegedly%20changed%20on%20the%20verbal%20directions%20of%20the%20Anantnag%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Bchange%20in%20building%20plan%5D%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20BOCA%20as%20per%20the%20Development%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20then-PDA%20CEO%20notes%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20law%20which%20governs%20the%20PDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20BOCA%20didn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20to%20approve%20the%20change%20in%20the%20terms%20of%20permission%20granted%20to%20th