that%20Korean%20companies%20have%20had%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20stability%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government.%20For%20example%2C%20while%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20was%20very%20open%20in%20attracting%20foreign%20investment%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20production%20process%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%20where%20companies%20have%20not%20received%20their%20incentives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolicies%20change%20quickly%20and%20easily%2C%20and%20after%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20firms%20have%20not%20received%20the%20incentives%20promised%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lee.%20This%20could%20hold%20back%20investors%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20noted%20that%20Lee%20did%20not%20cite%20specific%20instances%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20but%20as%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Ftechnology%2Fsamsung-may-lose-pli-sops-for-first-year-on-invoicing-issues%2Farticleshow%2F100712753.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewithheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20incentives%20claimed%20by%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20Ltd%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20scheme%20totalling%20Rs%20900%20crore%20on%20the%20sales%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%2C%20citing%20invoicing%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20advanced%20stage%20of%20discussions%20with%20Government%20of%20India%20on%20the%20incentive%20payout.%20Samsung%20is%20a%20committed%20partner%20of%20India%20for%20over%2026%20years.%20As%20the%20leading%20smartphone%20player%2C%20we%20have%20been%20working%20closely%20with%20various%20stakeholders%20to%20make%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Samsung%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffreebies-pli-scheme-manufacturing%5C%22%3EAre%20Government%20Freebies%20Under%20PLI%20Scheme%20Truly%20Necessary%20to%20Enhance%20Manufacturing%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20loopholes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20one%20of%20the%20initiatives%20under%20the%20flagship%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20Abhiyaan.%20The%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20creating%20more%20jobs%2C%20attracting%20greater%20investments%2C%20reducing%20imports%2C%20and%20making%20India%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20panacea%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20problems%2C%20several%20loopholes%20in%20the%20scheme%20are%20raising%20concerns%20over%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20May%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fcons-products%2Felectronics%2Findia-surpasses-rs-85000-cr-worth-mobile-phone-exports-in-fy23%2Farticleshow%2F99334570.cms%5C%22%3Esurpassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2410%20billion%20(Rs%2082%2C000%20crore)%20worth%20smartphone%20exports%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20in%20exports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fconsumer-durables-and-information-technology%2Fmobiles%2Findian-smartphone-export-likely-crossed-over-rs-82000-crore-in-fy-2022-2023%2F99204073%5C%22%3Ewas%20attributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20PLI%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Raghuram%20Rajan%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-mobile-phone-exports-driven-by-assembly-rather-than-domestic-manufacturing-raghuram-rajan%5C%22%3Eopined%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20boom%20in%20mobile%20phone%20exports%20might%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20concern%20as%20the%20growth%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20back%20of%20assembly%20rather%20than%20genuine%20manufacturing%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20key%20deficiency%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20that%20the%20subsidy%20is%20paid%20only%20for%20finishing%20the%20phone%20in%20India%2C%20not%20on%20how%20much%20value%20is%20added%20by%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20matters!%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20very%20little%20apart%20from%20assembly%20is%20done%20in%20India%2C%20though%20manufacturers%20claim%20they%20intend%20to%20do%20more%20in%20future.%20So%20India%20still%20imports%20much%20of%20what%20goes%20into%20the%20mobile%20phone%2C%20and%20when%20we%20correct%20for%20that%2C%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20maintain%20that%20net%20exports%20have%20gone%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20retired%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20professor%20Arun%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpli-scheme-subsidies-demand-shortage-jobs%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20despite%20a%20promise%20of%20increased%20profits%2C%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20has%20not%20gained%20momentum%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20demand.%20If%20one%20cannot%20sell%20more%2C%20the%20subsidy%20will%20also%20not%20accrue%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690537545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28141558%2Fravi-sharma-HCoHGXiDMpE-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsouth-korean-firms-havent-received-the-promised-incentives-as-part-of-pli-scheme-says-top-official%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20top%20official%20from%20the%20Korea%20International%20Trade%20Association%20has%20said%20that%20arbitrary%20policy%20changes%20by%20the%20government%20are%20a%20key%20concern%20for%20Korean%20companies%20investing%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsouth-korean-firms-havent-received-the-promised-incentives-as-part-of-pli-scheme-says-top-official%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20-%20Shiny%20But%20Shallow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBuilt%20upon%20a%20surfeit%20of%20stereotypes%2C%20Karan%20Johar's%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehinges%20on%20a%20pulpy%20Punjabi-Bengali%20culture%20clash%20that%20serves%20as%20a%20means%20to%20explore%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20relationships%2C%20the%20often-crushing%20pressures%20of%20family%20ties%20and%20the%20shackles%20of%20gender%20roles%20in%20a%20changed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20noises%20that%20the%20mawkish%20and%20musty%20melodrama%20makes%20is%20sporadically%20spot-on%2C%20but%20the%20film%2C%20overly%20keen%20to%20play%20to%20the%20gallery%20and%20take%20recourse%20to%20storytelling%20tics%20that%20feel%20out-of-date%2C%20lacks%20consistency%20of%20purpose.%20Parts%20of%20it%20are%20fun%20but%20most%20of%20it%20is%20marred%20by%20an%20undisguised%20urge%20to%20pontificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenplay%20is%20erratic%20-%20it%20goes%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20taking%20its%20eyes%20off%20the%20ball%20and%20hitting%20it%20out%20of%20the%20park%2C%20with%20the%20ratio%20tilted%20markedly%20towards%20the%20former%20-%20but%20the%20performances%20are%20robust%20enough%20to%20help%20the%20film%20paper%20over%20its%20creases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20written%20by%20Ishita%20Moitra%2C%20Shashank%20Khaitan%20and%20Sumit%20Roy%2C%20aims%20to%20deliver%20a%20mix%20of%20hearty%20laughs%20and%20'useful'%20marital%20advice.%20It%20makes%20rather%20heavy%20weather%20of%20both%20although%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20taking%20cracks%20at%20unmasking%20patriarchy%2C%20outdated%20notions%20of%20masculinity%20and%20cultural%20chauvinism%2C%20it%20does%20deliver%20a%20few%20pointed%20home%20truths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20takes%20away%20much%20of%20the%20film's%20sheen%20are%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20cliches.%20Faded%20chestnuts%20abound%20in%20this%20tale%20of%20modernity%20squaring%20off%20against%20tradition%20in%20a%20very%20physical%20form%20and%20in%20very%20obvious%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20side%20is%20Randhawa%20Paradise%2C%20a%20sprawling%20mansion%20somewhere%20in%20National%20Capital%20Region.%20On%20the%20other%20is%20Chatterjee%20House%2C%20a%20no%20less%20impressive%20bungalow%20in%20(as%20we%20are%20tangentially%20told)%20in%20South%20Delhi.%20The%20two%20families%20that%20reside%20in%20these%20buildings%20are%20so%20different%20from%20each%20other%20that%20they%20could%20be%20from%20different%20planets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20orthodox%20Punjabi%20business%20family%2C%20a%20matriarch%20(Jaya%20Bachchan)%20calls%20the%20shots%2C%20her%20arrogant%20son%20(Aamir%20Bashir)%20scowls%20and%20growls%20in%20perfect%20concert%20with%20her%20whims%2C%20but%20the%20other%20women%20in%20the%20household%20-%20the%20man's%20wife%20(Kshitee%20Jog)%20and%20daughter%20(Anjali%20Anand)%20have%20no%20agency.%20The%20Bengali%20brood%20is%20made%20up%20of%20three%20women%20from%20three%20generations%20and%20a%20man%20who%20makes%20a%20living%20as%20a%20Kathak%20guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6mdxy3zohEk%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPredictably%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20hackneyed%20ideas%20that%20are%20propounded%20by%20one%20of%20the%20two%20families%20are%20torn%20to%20shreds%20in%20the%20battle%20that%20erupts%20when%20a%20flashy%20Punjabi%20boy%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%20who%20wears%20his%20heart%20on%20his%20sleeves%20meets%20a%20sedate%20Bengali%20career%20girl%20(Alia%20Bhatt)%20with%20a%20Columbia%20University%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERocky%20Randhawa%20and%20Rani%20Chatterjee's%20love%20story%20sets%20off%20a%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20is%20entertaining%20to%20an%20extent%20till%20the%20point%20that%20the%20film%20refrains%20from%20taking%20itself%20too%20seriously.%20When%20it%20begins%20to%20strike%20'reformist'%20postures%20half%20way%20through%20and%20goes%20the%20whole%20hog%20with%20them%20post-intermission%2C%20it%20runs%20a%20touch%20ragged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paths%20of%20Rocky%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%2C%20the%20scion%20of%20a%20family%20that%20owns%20a%20Karol%20Bagh%20Market%20sweet%20shop%20famous%20for%20its%20desi%20ghee%20laddoos%20and%20Rani%20(Alia%20Bhatt)%2C%20a%20television%20news%20anchor%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20parents%20(Churni%20Ganguly%20an%20Tota%20Roychowdhury)%20and%20grandmother%20(Shabana%20Azmi)%2C%20cross%20in%20unusual%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERocky%20goes%20looking%20for%20Jamini%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20married%20woman%20who%20his%20dementia-afflicted%20grandfather%20(Dharmendra)%20met%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekavi%20sammelan%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Shimla%20in%20the%20late%201970s%20and%20still%20remembers.%20He%20hopes%20a%20reunion%20would%20revive%20his%20badly%20impaired%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamini%20is%20of%20course%20Rani's%20grandmother%2C%20whose%20brief%20encounter%20with%20Rocky's%20grandpa%20was%20a%20weeklong%20affair%20that%20had%20a%20lifelong%20impact.%20The%20septuagenarian%20lady%20regrets%20not%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20turn%20her%20back%20on%20her%20marriage%20to%20be%20with%20her%20lover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20it%20would%20take%20the%20involvement%20of%20their%20two%20families%20to%20get%20their%20impending%20marriage%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20Rani%20and%20Rocky%20decide%20to%20spend%20time%20in%20each%20other's%20homes%20to%20test%20the%20waters.%20At%20both%20ends%2C%20the%20beginning%20is%20frosty.%20How%20the%20thaw%20begins%20and%20pans%20out%20in%20the%20two%20households%20as%20Rani%20and%20Rocky%20try%20to%20build%20bridges%20against%20heavy%20odds%20is%20what%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20film%20revolves%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20filmed%20on%20lavish%20(when%20not%20outright%20garish)%20sets%2C%20deals%20with%20regrets%20and%20renewals%2C%20accusations%20and%20apologies%2C%20showdowns%20and%20patch-ups.%20All%20its%20inferences%20and%20truisms%20are%20delivered%20in%20unsubtle%2C%20simplistic%20ways%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20ensuring%20that%20no%20'message'%20that%20it%20delivers%20goes%20abegging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlitzy%20and%20rambunctious%20-that%20is%20the%20least%20you'd%20expect%20a%20Karan%20Johar%20movie%20to%20be%20-%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20peppy%20songs%20composed%20by%20Pritam%20(with%20linguistically%20and%20idiomatically%20varied%20lyrics%20by%20Amitabh%20Bhattacharya)%2C%20a%20range%20of%20retro%20numbers%20(to%20highlight%20a%20love%20affair%20from%20the%20past%20as%20well%20as%20underline%20the%20differences%20in%20ethos%20that%20separate%20the%20younger%20lovers)%2C%20some%20rough%20and%20ready%20humour%2C%20and%20a%20generous%20springling%20of%20caramelised%2C%20sickly%20sweet%20pearls%20of%20wisdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20screen%20and%20off%20it%2C%20flamboyance%20comes%20easy%20to%20Ranveer%20Singh.%20There%20is%20nobody%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20industry%20who%20could%20have%20pulled%20off%20Rocky%20as%20well%20as%20he%20does.%20Is%20his%20exuberance%20toned%20down%20in%20a%20way%20that%20generates%20coiled%2C%20consistent%20energy%3F%20Well%2C%20almost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20strikes%20the%20right%20notes%20in%20the%20role%20of%20a%20girl%20who%20embraces%20her%20beliefs%20with%20confidence%20and%20confronts%20all%20the%20imperfections%20in%20her%20and%20in%20the%20people%20around%20her%20without%20letting%20any%20of%20it%20get%20the%20better%20of%20her.%20She%20is%20the%20real%20star%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmendra%20delivers%20a%20performance%20that%20you%20cannot%20but%20fall%20in%20love%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20supporting%20performances%20are%20all%20from%20the%20topmost%20drawer.%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20as%20the%20hero's%20testy%20grandmother%20who%20yields%20no%20ground%20to%20anybody%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20in%20the%20role%20of%20the%20heroine's%20spirited%20but%20soft-hearted%20granny%20are%20terrific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurni%20Ganguly%2C%20cast%20as%20the%20flowery%20English-spouting%20mother%20who%20has%20instilled%20a%20spirit%20of%20independence%20in%20her%20daughter%2C%20has%20far%20less%20to%20do%20but%20the%20impact%20that%20she%20has%20on%20the%20film%20is%20second%20to%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20carries%20off%20the%20role%20of%20an%20accomplished%20kathak%20dancer%20redefining%20the%20boundaries%20of%20maleness%20with%20noteworthy%20aplomb.%20Aamir%20Bashir%20does%20an%20impressive%20job%20of%20presenting%20the%20ill-advisedly%20confrontational%20face%20of%20masculinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETu%20hai%20kya%2C%20yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20That%20is%20a%20question%20that%20Rani%20poses%20to%20Rocky%20a%20number%20of%20times.%20Exactly%20our%20question.%20Not%20to%20Rocky%2C%20but%20to%20the%20film.%20In%20one%20scene%2C%20Shabana%20Azmi's%20character%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20request%20made%20at%20a%20wedding%20to%20her%20dancer-son%20to%20perform%20a%20number%20from%20Devdas%2C%20says%3A%20So%20typical!%20The%20film%20need%20not%20have%20been%20so%20typical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20subversion%20that%20runs%20through%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20pretty%20boldly%20at%20that%20(as%20in%20the%20lingerie%20store%20sequence%20or%20in%20the%20discussion%20on%20being%20a%20male%20Kathak%20dancer)%2C%20the%20film%20is%20a%20shiny%20but%20shallow%20family%20drama%20that%20uses%20disappointingly%20obsolete%20methods%20to%20serve%20up%20contemporary%2C%20pertinent%20theories%20about%20the%20need%20to%20be%20mindful%20in%20love%2C%20loyalty%20and%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690537500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Flr00k218_alia-_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-review-shiny-but-shallow-family-drama-2-stars-4248187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%20Review%3A%20There%20is%20nobody%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20industry%20who%20could%20have%20pulled%20off%20Rocky%20as%20well%20as%20Ranveer%20Singh%20does.%20Alia%20Bhatt%20strikes%20the%20right%20notes%20in%20the%20role%20of%20a%20girl%20who%20embraces%20her%20beliefs%20with%20confidence%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-review-shiny-but-shallow-family-drama-2-stars-4248187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-review-shiny-but-shallow-family-drama-2-stars-4248187%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frocky-aur-rani-kii-prem-kahaani-review-shiny-but-shallow-family-drama-2-stars-4248187%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%205%20Years%20in%20Jail%2C%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%20and%20Arun%20Ferreira%20Get%20Bail%20in%20Elgar%20Parishad%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28135451%2FUntitled-design-20-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%20five%20years%20after%20rights%20activists%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%20and%C2%A0Arun%20Ferreira%20were%20arrested%20for%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20today%2C%20July%2028%2C%20ordered%20for%20their%20release%20on%20bail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20observed%20that%20the%20material%20evidence%20available%20against%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20justify%20their%20continuous%20detention%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBooked%20under%20the%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%2C%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20last%20year.%20Their%20bail%20applications%20had%20earlier%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20special%20NIA%20court%20and%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court.%20Senior%20lawyers%20Rebecca%20John%20and%20R.%20Basant%20had%20highlighted%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20the%20commencement%20of%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20grounds%20in%20the%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20court%20today%2C%20while%20granting%20them%20bail%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20fact%20that%20almost%20five%20years%20have%20lapsed%20since%20they%20(Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira)%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%E2%80%A6%20the%20appellants%20have%20made%20out%20a%20case%20for%20granting%20of%20bail.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lawyers%20had%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20against%20the%20arrested%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20a%20long%20wait%20for%20Arun%20and%20the%20family.%20We%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ferreira%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Jennifer%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20controversial%20case%20and%20investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20registered%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%20in%20January%202018%20and%20later%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20since%20the%20very%20start.%20While%20the%20state%20had%20initially%20claimed%20that%2016%20persons%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20including%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20%E2%80%93%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Cprovoking%E2%80%9D%20the%20gathered%20crowd%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20with%20their%20speeches%20and%20triggering%20violence%20on%20the%20200th-anniversary%20celebration%20of%20the%20battle%20of%20Bhima%20Koregaon%2C%20they%20were%20later%20accused%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Curban%20Naxals%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20claims%20of%20their%20alleged%20association%20with%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%20is%20based%20on%20purported%20emails%20and%20other%20evidence%20allegedly%20retrieved%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20belonging%20to%20the%20accused.%20These%20claims%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20challenged%20by%20many%20independent%20forensic%20organisations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20investigation%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felgar-parishad-case-surveillance-pegasus%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20partner%20news%20organisations%20revealed%20that%20at%20least%20nine%20numbers%20belonged%20to%20eight%20activists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20academics%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20were%20either%20persons%20of%20interest%20or%20forensically%20identified%20as%20having%20been%20targeted%20by%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware.%20A%20Massachusetts-based%20digital%20forensics%20firm%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArsenal%20Consulting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20later%20confirmed%20at%20least%20one%20phone%20%E2%80%93%20belonging%20to%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist%20Rona%20Wilson%20%E2%80%93%20was%20definitely%20infected%20by%20the%20malicious%20spyware.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20are%20Sudhir%20Dhawale%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20Mumbai-based%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%3B%20Mahesh%20Raut%2C%20a%20young%20activist%20from%20Gadchiroli%20who%20worked%20on%20displacement%3B%20Shoma%20Sen%2C%20who%20had%20been%20head%20of%20the%20English%20literature%20department%20at%20Nagpur%20University%3B%20advocates%20Arun%20Ferreira%20and%20Sudha%20Bharadwaj%3B%20writer%20Varavara%20Rao%3B%20activist%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%3B%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist%20Rona%20Wilson%3B%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20a%20UAPA%20expert%20and%20lawyer%20from%20Nagpur%3B%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20the%20late%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%3B%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20scholar%3B%20academic%20Anand%20Teltumbde%3B%20civil%20liberties%20activist%20Gautam%20Navlakha%3B%20and%20members%20of%20the%20cultural%20group%2C%20Kabir%20Kala%20Manch%3A%20Sagar%20Gorkhe%2C%20Ramesh%20Ghaichor%20and%20Jyoti%20Jagtap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-arrested-activists-status%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETeltumbde%2C%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Rao%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fill-treatment-of-stan-swamy-in-jail-should-shake-foundation-of-democracy-fellow-prisoner%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESwamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20died%20last%20year%20allegedly%20due%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20negligence%20and%20failure%20to%20provide%20him%20with%20adequate%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20other%20accused%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20Sen%20and%20Jagtap%20%E2%80%93%20have%20also%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Cou