ry%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690534397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102199060%2Cimgsize-549135.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-playing-role-of-a-great-conductor-for-semiconductor-industry-ticking-all-right-boxes-modi%2Farticleshow%2F102198953.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PARTH%20SHASTRI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-playing-role-of-a-great-conductor-for-semiconductor-industry-ticking-all-right-boxes-modi%2Farticleshow%2F102198953.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20Calls%20for%20Ban%20on%20Live-in%20Relationships%20to%20%E2%80%98Protect%20Women%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28125747%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-12.57.20-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Ajay%20Pratap%20Singh%20on%20Wednesday%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20illegalise%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbjp-mp-calls-for-ban-on-live-in-relationships-8862180%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20addressing%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20Special%20Mentions%20when%20he%20cited%20a%20recent%20murder%20case%20of%20one%20Saraswati%20Vaidya%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20was%20allegedly%20killed%20by%20her%20live-in%20partner%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20his%20plea%2C%20Singh%20cited%20WHO%20data%20and%20said%20that%20nearly%2038%25%20of%20all%20murders%20of%20women%20in%20the%20world%20are%20by%20their%20intimate%20partners%20%E2%80%93%20without%20clarifying%20that%20the%20WHO%20data%20includes%20those%20who%20are%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMarriage%20and%20family%20ties%20are%20a%20cultural%20heritage%20in%20India.%20Our%20religious%20scriptures%20and%20customs%20do%20not%20grant%20recognition%20to%20live-ins%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbjp-mp-calls-for-ban-on-live-in-relationships-8862180%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20recognised%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbjp-mp-calls-for-ban-on-live-in-relationships-8862180%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20said%20that%20Indian%20society%20considers%20it%20unethical%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20illegal.%20I%20believe%20if%20this%20is%20unethical%2C%20then%20it%20should%20be%20illegal%2C%20too.%20The%20government%20should%20take%20cognisance%20of%20this%20and%20bring%20a%20law%20so%20that%20this%20subculture%20can%20be%20stopped%20and%20women%20can%20be%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-5)%2C%20nearly%2030%25%20or%20every%201%20in%203%20married%20women%20experienced%20domestic%20or%20sexual%20violence%20and%203.1%25%20pregnant%20women%20suffered%20physical%20violence%20during%20their%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20February%202023%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-finds-working-of-domestic-violence-act-dismal-4-7-lakh-cases-pending%2Farticleshow%2F98220736.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ecalled%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20domestic%20violence%20act%20%E2%80%9Cdismal%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20there%20were%204.7%20lakh%20domestic%20violence%20cases%20pending%20across%20801%20districts%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690534239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2