0for%20the%20return%20of%20arms%20taken%20forcibly%20or%20stolen%20from%20armouries%20and%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%E2%80%99s%20report%20says%20that%20the%20police%20inspector%2C%20Michael%20Yanthan%2C%20was%20allegedly%20paid%20Rs%204.25%20lakh%20to%20get%20the%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fnagaland-to-probe-illegal-ammo-transport-by-cop%2Farticle67128050.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Nagaland%20police%20have%20constituted%20a%20panel%20headed%20by%20an%20inspector-general%20of%20police%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20on%20July%2010%2C%20when%20Nagaland%20Police%20stopped%20a%20car%20at%20Chumukeidma%20in%20Nagaland.%20The%20car%20had%20three%20bags%20of%20rice%2C%20in%20which%20were%20%E2%80%9C2%2C500%20types%20of%20ammunition%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%20Yanthan%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20police%20central%20store%20at%20Chumukeidma%2C%20was%20thus%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20quoted%20an%20anonymous%20police%20officer%20who%20indicated%20to%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20stolen%20ammunition%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20sold%20in%20adjoining%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland%E2%80%99s%20Director-General%20of%20Police%2C%20Rupin%20Sharma%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20conspiracy%20angle%20of%20the%20crime%20will%20only%20be%20revealed%20after%20the%20probe%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690533658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-nagaland-police-ammunition-stealing-transporting%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20being%20assumed%20that%20the%20ammunition%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20Manipur%20where%20ethnic%20violence%20has%20continued%20for%20almost%20three%20months%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-nagaland-police-ammunition-stealing-transporting%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Engaging%20In%20Theatrics%5C%22%3A%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%20Face%20Off%20In%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20week%20of%20sloganeering%20and%20repeated%20disruptions%20over%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20issue%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20witnessed%20a%20marked%20escalation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20showdown%20between%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20and%20Trinamool%20Congess%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairman%20accused%20the%20TMC%20MP%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bengaging%20in%20theatrics%26quot%3B%20a%20habit%2C%20inviting%20a%20strong%20objection%20from%20Mr%20O'Brien%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20quoting%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20House%20and%20demanding%20a%20serious%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spat%20occurred%20when%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20was%20addressing%20the%20members%20of%20the%20House%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20repeated%20disruptions%20in%20the%20House%20do%20not%20evoke%20respect%20among%20the%20people.%20He%20also%20spoke%20of%20how%20he%20was%20getting%20inputs%20from%20all%20over%2C%20indicating%20%26quot%3Balarming%20concern%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20received%2047%20notices%20today%20under%20Rule%20267%20with%20respect%20to%20expression%20of%20their%20concern%20over%20the%20prevailing%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20is%20a%20situation%20that%20I%20have%20countenanced%20during%20the%20entire%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chairman%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20inputs%20from%20all%20over%2C%20they%20indicate%20worrisome%2C%20alarming%20concern.%20I%20would%20therefore%20appeal%20to%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20House%20to%20rise%20above%20partisan%20interests%20and%20work%20in%20a%20manner%20so%20that%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%2C%20which%20I%20have%20agreed%20to%2C%20can%20take%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Chairman%20was%20pointing%20to%20the%20precedent%20of%20very%20few%20Rule%20267%20notices%20being%20accepted%20and%20stating%20that%20the%20entire%20nation%20looks%20at%20proceedings%20in%20Parliament%2C%20he%20was%20interrupted%20by%20Mr%20O'Brien%2C%20who%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20aware%20of%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20escalated%20quickly%20after%20that%2C%20with%20the%20Chairman%20asking%20Mr%20O'Brien%20to%20%26quot%3Blend%20your%20ears%20and%20take%20your%20seat%26quot%3B.%20When%20the%20TMC%20MP%20continued%20to%20speak%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20it%20has%20become%20your%20habit%20to%20engage%20in%20theatrics.%20You%20rise%20every%20time%2C%20you%20think%20it%20is%20your%20prerogative.%20The%20minimum%20thing%20which%20you%20can%20exemplify%20is%20to%20show%20respect%20to%20the%20chair.%20If%20I%20am%20saying%20something%2C%20you%20rise%20and%20create%20theatrics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20invited%20a%20strong%20reaction%20from%20the%20TMC%20MP%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTheatrics%3F%20I%20object%20to%20the%20word%20theatrics.%20I%20am%20only%20quoting%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20House.%20We%20want%20a%20serious%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%20under%20Rule%20267%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20emergency%20provision%2C%20given%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20issue%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20angry%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20then%20asked%20Mr%20O'Brien%20not%20to%20thump%20the%20table.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20thump%20it.%20It%20is%20not%20theatrics.%20I%20will%20call%20the%20leaders.%20We%20can't%20suffer%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20then%20adjourned%20the%20House%20till%20Monday%20even%20as%20the%20visibly%20angry%20MP%20continued%20to%20wave%20his%20hands%20and%20speak%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20been%20pressing%20for%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267%2C%20which%20gives%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20special%20power%20to%20suspend%20the%20pre-decided%20agenda%20of%20the%20House%2C%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotions%20moved%20under%20this%20rule%20have%20rarely%20been%20accepted.%20Parliamentary%20records%20show%20that%20discussions%20under%20the%20rule%20were%20allowed%20only%2011%20times%20between%201990%20and%202016.%20The%20last%20instance%20was%20in%202016%2C%20when%20then%20Chairman%20Hamid%20Ansari%20had%20allowed%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bdemonetisation%20of%20currency%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20refused%20a%20discussion%20under%20Rule%20267%20and%20offered%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20under%20Rule%20176%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%2C%20but%20has%20no%20provision%20for%20a%20formal%20motion%20or%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690532820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fdlbsa5q8_derek-dhankhar-rajya-sabha-650_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fengaging-in-theatrics-jagdeep-dhankhar-derek-obrien-face-off-in-parliament-4247968%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20week%20of%20sloganeering%20and%20repeated%20disruptions%20over%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20issue%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20witnessed%20a%20marked%20escalation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20showdown%20between%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20and%20Trinamool%20Congess%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fengaging-in-theatrics-jagdeep-dhankhar-derek-obrien-face-off-in-parliament-4247968%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fengaging-in-theatrics-jagdeep-dhankhar-derek-obrien-face-off-in-parliament-4247968%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fengaging-in-theatrics-jagdeep-dhankhar-derek-obrien-face-off-in-parliament-4247968%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20Director%20Extension%3A%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20Against%20the%20Rule%20of%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28133058%2Fsk-mishra-supreme-court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findconlawphil.wordpress.com%2F2023%2F07%2F17%2Fthe-limits-of-institutional-independence-the-supreme-courts-ed-director-judgment%2F%5C%22%3Eprevious%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20recent%20judgment%20involving%20the%20tenure%20extensions%20granted%20to%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20I%20had%20wondered%20%E2%80%93%20somewhat%20rhetorically%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20have%20any%20respect%20for%20itself%2C%20and%20for%20its%20own%20orders%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20context%20for%20this%20was%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20found%20that%20the%20ED%20director%20had%20been%20kept%20in%20his%20role%2C%20in%20flagrant%20breach%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20own%20orders%2C%20for%20a%20period%20of%20one%20year%20and%20eight%20months%3B%20but%20far%20from%20visiting%20any%20consequences%20upon%20the%20executive%2C%20the%20SC%20allowed%20the%20director%20to%20%3Cem%3Estay%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20his%20role%20until%20the%20end%20of%20July%2C%20to%20facilitate%20%E2%80%9Ca%20smooth%20transition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20light%20of%20fresh%20events%2C%20one%20must%20now%20not%20only%20wonder%20whether%20the%20SC%20has%20any%20respect%20for%20itself%20and%20its%20own%20orders%2C%20but%20whether%20it%20has%20respect%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20executive%20filed%20an%20application%20asking%20for%20an%20%3Cem%3Eextension%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20the%20ED%20director%20until%20the%20end%20of%20October%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20input%20was%20needed%20for%20the%20global%20FATF%20review.%20Notice%20the%20breathtaking%20audacity%20here%3A%20far%20from%20being%20chastened%20by%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20holding%20that%20it%20had%20breached%20a%20direct%20order%20not%20once%2C%20but%20twice%20(in%20granting%20the%20ED%20director%20two%20extensions)%2C%20the%20executive%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20sanction%20a%20%3Cem%3Efurther%20%3C%2Fem%3Eextension%20of%20a%20continuing%20illegality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20think%20that%2C%20in%20a%20jurisdiction%20that%20is%20formally%20committed%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20and%20to%20the%20principle%20that%20government%20is%20not%20above%20the%20law%2C%20such%20an%20application%20would%20not%20only%20be%20dismissed%2C%20but%20that%20punitive%20costs%20would%20be%20imposed%20upon%20the%20executive%20for%20wasting%20judicial%20time%20(after%20all%2C%20the%20judiciary%20has%20been%20quite%20eager%20of%20late%20to%20impose%20costs%20on%20petitioners%20for%20wasting%20its%20time).%20One%20would%20be%20wrong.%20After%20a%20brief%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sanctioned%20a%20further%20extension%20to%20the%20ED%20directors%E2%80%99%20tenure%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D%2C%20until%20the%20middle%20of%20September%20(half%20the%20time%20the%20executive%20had%20asked%20for%20%E2%80%93%20as%20if%20what%20was%20happening%20was%20a%20negotiation%20for%20a%20salary%20increment%2C%20and%20not%20a%20serious%20issue%20involving%20the%20rule%20of%20law).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20today%20sent%20a%20signal%20that%20in%20India%2C%20there%20is%20one%20entity%20%E2%80%93%20and%20one%20entity%20alone%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20entitled%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20its%20own%20wrong%2C%20not%20once%2C%20not%20twice%2C%20but%20many%20times%20over%3B%20and%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20entity%20that%20can%20refuse%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20and%20not%20only%20get%20away%20with%20it%2C%20but%20benefit%20from%20it.%20That%20entity%20is%20the%20Union%20government.%20One%20would%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20imagine%20a%20more%20destructive%20or%20damaging%20undermining%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20consequences%20follow.%20One%20is%20that%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20order%20will%20only%20further%20embolden%20the%20executive%20to%20treat%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20law%20as%20optional.%20Because%20not%20only%20are%20there%20no%20judicial%20sanctions%20for%20breach%2C%20breach%20is%20actively%20%3Cem%3Eincentivised.%20%3C%2Fem%3EIn%20such%20a%20circumstance%2C%20who%20would%20%3Cem%3Enot%20%3C%2Fem%3Etake%20advantage%20of%20the%20impunity%20that%20has%20been%20so%20generously%20offered%3F%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20a%20more%20long-term%20consequence%2C%20although%20as%20troubling.%20If%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20unable%20%E2%80%93%20or%20unwilling%20%E2%80%93%20to%20enforce%20its%20own%20previous%2C%20direct%20orders%20(not%20once%2C%20not%20twice%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3Emany%20%3C%2Fem%3Etimes)%20in%20the%20face%20of%20executive%20recalcitrance%2C%20then%20what%20hope%20%E2%80%93%20if%20any%20%E2%80%93%20ought%20citizens%20to%20have%20in%20its%20ability%20or%20willingness%20to%20adjudicate%20cases%20involving%20serious%20and%20far-reaching%20constitutional%20breaches%20by%20the%20executive%3F%20Would%20not%20such%20cases%20and%20constitutional%20challenges%20be%20effectively%20turned%20into%20a%20formality%2C%20where%20the%20outcome%20is%20known%2C%20and%20everyone%20simply%20goes%20through%20the%20motions%3F%20We%20are%20aware%20of%20jurisdictions%20where%20that%20is%20the%20case%3B%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20orders%20such%20as%20today%E2%80%99s%20raise%20a%20disquieting%20sense%20of%20proximity.%20After%20all%2C%20as%20a%20senior%20counsel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frethinkaadhaar.in%2Fblog%2F2017%2F5%2F4%2Fsenior-advocate-datar-aadhaar-is-like-building-a-bridge-and-then-looking-for-a-river-it-is-hunting-for-problems-to-make-itself-relevant%5C%22%3Eonce%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20court%20%E2%80%93%20in%20what%20seems%20an%20eternity%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cas%20nightfall%20does%20not%20come%20at%20once%2C%20neither%20does%20oppression.%20In%20both%20instances%2C%20there%20is%20a%20twilight%20when%20everything%20remains%20seemingly%20unchanged.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20such%20twilight%20that%20we%20all%20must%20be%20most%20aware%20of%20change%20in%20the%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findconlawphil.wordpress.com%2F2023%2F07%2F27%2Fthe-ed-director-judgment-ii-the-supreme-court-against-the-rule-of-law%2F%5C%22%3Eauthor%E2%80%99s%20blog%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fgautam-bhatia%5C%22%3EGautam%20Bhatia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690531812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28133058%2Fsk-mishra-supreme-court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-director-extension-supreme-court-respect-rule-of-law%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20extended%20S.K.%20Mishra's%20tenure%20until%20the%20middle%20of%20September%20at%20the%20executive's%20request.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20court%20has%20sent%20a%20signal%20that%20in%20India%2C%20there%20is%20one%20entity%20%E2%80%93%20and%20one%20entity%20alone%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20entitled%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20its%20own%20wrong%2C%20not%20once%2C%20not%20twice%2C%20but%20many%20times%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-director-extension-supreme-court-respect-rule-of-law%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20New%20%E2%80%98Black%20Market%20of%20Power%E2%80%99%20in%20Naya%20Bharat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28132720%2FModi-Adani.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20never%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20questioned%20extensively%20by%20anyone%20except%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzKO0-J7bDcQ%5C%22%3EAkshay%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(yes%2C%20yes%2C%20the%20very%20same%20man%20who%20can%20be%20seen%20these%20days%20marketing%20bathroom%20toilet%20cleaning%20products%20and%20mouth%20freshener)%2C%20an%20amateur%20psychologist%20is%20at%20a%20distinct%20disadvantage%20trying%20to%20profile%20his%20persona.%20But%20anyone%20listening%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Ftext-of-prime-minister-narendra-modi-s-speech-at-inauguration-of-international-exhibition-cum-convention-centre-iecc-complex-at-pragati-maidan-in-new-delhi-572394%5C%22%3Eself-serving%20proclamations%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2026%20will%20have%20no%20difficulty%20in%20concluding%20that%20the%20man%20has%20irreversibly%20slipped%20into%20a%20delusional%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CModi%20ki%20guarantee%E2%80%9D%20spiel%20that%20India%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20my%20third%20term%E2%80%9D%20had%20already%20been%20pre-empted%20a%20week%20earlier%20by%20Gautam%20Adani.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindenburg-report-targeted-misinformation-allegations-discredited-adani-123071800271_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20controversial%20oligarch%20had%20told%20the%20Adani%20Enterprises%E2%80%99%20AGM%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20July%2018%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20economic%20cycles%20are%20getting%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20forecast%2C%20there%20is%20little%20doubt%20that%20India%20%E2%80%93%20already%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%205th%20largest%20economy%20%E2%80%93%20will%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third%20largest%20economy%20well%20before%202030.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20exactly%20the%20timetable%20the%20prime%20minister%20unveiled%20to%20his%20Pragati%20Maidan%20audience.%20Just%20to%20round%20up%20the%20argument%2C%20the%20Hindenburg-bitten%20tycoon%20had%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20well%20understood%20that%20for%20any%20economy%20to%20implement%20policy%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20growth%2C%20a%20stable%20government%20is%20critical.%E2%80%9D%20And%2C%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmy%20belief%20in%20the%20growth%20story%20of%20our%20%3Ci%3Ematrabhumi%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20never%20been%20stronger.%E2%80%9D%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20whether%20any%20kind%20of%20%3Ci%3Ejugalbandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20at%20work%2C%20yet%20the%20convergence%20between%20the%20July%2018%20argument%20and%20the%20July%2026%20assertion%20leaves%20very%20little%20to%20the%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20convergence%20was%20anticipated%20about%2080%20years%20ago%20by%20Walter%20Benjamin%2C%20the%20celebrated%20Jewish%20dissident%20in%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20when%20he%20talked%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fusers.clas.ufl.edu%2Fburt%2FPROUST2021INCOMPLETENOVEL%2Fwalter-benjamin-selected-writings-volume-2-part-1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cblack%20market%20of%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20As%20Benjamin%20conceptualised%20it%2C%20this%20black%20market%20was%20characterised%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccorrelation%20of%20money%20and%20power%E2%80%9D%2C%20so%20evident%20in%20the%20Germany%20of%20the%201930s%20when%20all%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20industrialists%20had%20lined%20up%20behind%20the%20brutal%20practitioners%20of%20National%20Socialism.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20century%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20has%20already%20manifested%20itself%20in%20many%20countries%20where%20the%20economy%20is%20controlled%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20strong%20man%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20politically%20connected%20oligarchs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20we%20have%20our%20own%2C%20slightly%20refined%2C%20version%20because%20we%20have%20this%20little%20irritant%20called%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20which%20obliges%20the%20black%20marketeers%20of%20power%20to%20go%20through%20the%20motion%20of%20securing%20public%20support%20for%20their%20%E2%80%98growth%20model%E2%80%99.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20ruling%20clique%20is%20concerned%2C%20elections%20are%20a%20necessary%20nuisance.%20Not%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20cohorts%20are%20daunted%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20to%20contest%20elections.%20Like%20Lionel%20Messi%20proclaimed%2C%20after%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20for%20Argentina%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20what%20to%20do%20in%20every%20moment.%20We%20know%20how%20to%20win%20a%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20team%20from%20Gujarat%20too%20knows%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20winning%20mandates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20as%20the%20economy%20becomes%20more%20and%20more%20inequitable%20on%20their%20watch%2C%20the%20new%20rulers%20of%20Naya%20Bharat%20know%20how%20to%20seduce%20the%20%3Ci%3Eplebes%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20professional%20phrase-makers%20have%20already%20coined%20the%20lilting%20rhyme%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EPai%2C%20pai%2C%20gharib%20ki%20bhali%3C%2Fi%3E%20(Every%20paisa%20in%20the%20poor%E2%80%99s%20interests).%E2%80%9D%20The%20new%20oligarchs%20of%20Naya%20Bharat%20will%2C%20of%20course%2C%20permit%20themselves%20a%20sardonic%20smile.%20Indeed%2C%20a%20cocksure%20prime%20minister%20has%20already%20declared%20himself%20the%20winner%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInherent%20in%20this%20extravagant%20claim%20is%20a%20warning%20to%20all%20those%20who%20have%20a%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20ensure%20fairness%20in%20the%20system%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20not%20to%20take%20their%20mandate%20of%20protecting%20norms%20seriously.%20Instead%2C%20they%20must%20be%20prepared%20to%20overlook%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20brazenness%20because%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20contest%20is%20pre-ordained%2C%20if%20not%20pre-arranged.%20A%20bully%E2%80%99s%20perfect%20boast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boast%20comes%20naturally%20because%20beyond%20the%20desi%20oligarchs%2C%20the%20global%20moneyed%20elite%20sees%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%20an%20opportunity%20to%20grab%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20action%20for%20itself.%20Of%20this%20global%20segment%2C%20the%20arms-sellers%20and%20dealers%20are%20the%20most%20visible.%20This%20exotic%20and%20mysterious%20band%20of%20businessmen%20have%20perfected%20their%20tool-kit%20for%20trapping%20third%20world%20leaders%20in%20a%20seductive%20bubble%2C%20enticing%20them%20with%20illusions%20of%20power%20and%20potency.%20After%20his%20recent%20massive%20weapons%20deals%20with%20the%20Americans%20and%20the%20French%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20can%20be%20counted%20upon%20to%20reclaim%20his%20%E2%80%9856-inch%E2%80%99%20status%20by%20asserting%20that%20he%20has%20bolstered%20national%20defence%20as%20never%20before%20and%20has%20unprecedentedly%20strengthened%20the%20capabilities%20of%20our%20valiant%20soldiers%20to%20take%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20he%20could%20well%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20(with%20its%20earlier%20UPA%20and%20now%20INDIA%20coalition)%20of%20neglecting%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20forces%20and%20for%20short-changing%20the%20brave%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20%E2%80%98strongmen%E2%80%99%20need%20to%20remain%20%E2%80%98strong%E2%80%99%20by%20procuring%20%E2%80%98cutting-edge%E2%80%99%20weapons%20systems%2C%20just%20as%20the%20arms%20industry%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20needs%20to%20sell%20their%20ever-expensive%20war%20toys.%20John%20Bolton%2C%20one%20of%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20advisers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FlTAA8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealluded%20to%20the%20phenomenon%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSales%20of%20weapons%20systems%20are%20an%20important%20way%20the%20U.S.%20strengthens%20its%20Asian%20allies%2C%20as%20%5BFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%5D%20Macron%20understands.%20Furious%20at%20losing%20a%20submarine%20deal%20with%20Australia%20to%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Britain%2C%20he%20celebrated%20Bastille%20Day%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20announcing%20beforehand%20some%20%249%20billion%20in%20weapons%20sales.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20perhaps%20now%20easy%20to%20understand%20why%20Modi%20has%20not%20found%20the%20time%20or%20the%20inclination%20to%20visit%20a%20burning%20Manipur.%20All%20this%20time%2C%20he%20was%20soaking%20in%20the%20pomp%20and%20spectacle%20of%20%E2%80%98state%20visits%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20US%20and%20France.%20The%20fabled%20event%20manager%20has%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20mesmerised%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98events%E2%80%99%20staged%20by%20other%20managers.%20Mentally%20he%20had%20travelled%20as%20far%20away%20as%20he%20could%20from%20the%20ugliness%20that%20is%20eating%20away%20Manipur%20society%20and%20political%20order.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20the%20vast%20surveillance%20state%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20moral%20shame%20so%20painfully%20captured%20in%20a%20video.%20If%20he%20had%20been%20told%20about%20the%20video%20or%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20distracted%3B%20if%20he%20did%20not%20know%20of%20it%2C%20the%20pretorian%20guard%20would%20not%20have%20wanted%20to%20spoil%20his%20mood%20as%20he%20was%20being%20serenaded%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20And%2C%20now%20it%20is%20too%20late%20because%20he%20simply%20cannot%20acknowledge%20that%20his%20trusted%20home%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20mess%20of%20a%20delicate%20corner%20of%20India.%20A%20few%20weeks%20of%20moral%20outrage%20by%20bleeding-heart%20liberals%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20aura%20of%20a%20colossus%20sure-footedly%20striding%20the%20world%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20politician%20who%20relishes%20confrontation%2C%20Modi%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20talk%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20Manipur%20shame%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20media%20can%20be%20relied%20upon%20to%20reaffirm%20his%20credentials%20as%20the%20master%20of%20narratives.%20But%20in%20his%20delusional%20mode%2C%20Modi%20need%20not%20forget%20that%20the%20final%20narrative%20is%20written%20by%20the%20voter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690531287000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28132720%2FModi-Adani.jpg%22%2C%22ori