rabad%20flight%20took%20off%20without%20one%20of%20their%20passengers%20-%20Karnataka%20Governor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairasia-flight-leaves-behind-karnataka-governor-airlines-launches-probe-4247741%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairasia-flight-leaves-behind-karnataka-governor-airlines-launches-probe-4247741%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fairasia-flight-leaves-behind-karnataka-governor-airlines-launches-probe-4247741%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22H-1B%20Visa%3A%202nd%20Lottery%20Round%20To%20Be%20Held%20This%20Year%2C%20Says%20US%20Authority%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20second%20round%20of%20random%20lottery%20selection%20for%20the%20much%20sought-after%20H-1B%20visas%20for%20fiscal%202024%20will%20soon%20begin%20after%20it%20was%20determined%20that%20%26quot%3Badditional%20registrations%26quot%3B%20need%20to%20be%20selected%20to%20reach%20the%20numerical%20allocations%2C%20the%20US%20federal%20immigration%20agency%20has%20announced%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20could%20benefit%20more%20Indian%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20will%20select%20the%20additional%20registrations%20from%20the%20previously%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20using%20a%20random%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20USCIS%20conducted%20an%20initial%20random%20selection%20of%20properly%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20(FY)%202024%20H-1B%20cap%2C%20including%20for%20beneficiaries%20eligible%20for%20the%20advanced%20degree%20exemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20those%20petitioners%20with%20selected%20registrations%20for%20FY%202024%20are%20eligible%20to%20file%20H-1B%20cap-subject%20petitions.%20The%20initial%20filing%20period%20for%20those%20with%20selected%20registrations%20for%20FY%202024%20was%20from%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20through%20June%2030%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20is%20a%20non-immigrant%20visa%20that%20allows%20US%20companies%20to%20employ%20foreign%20workers%20in%20speciality%20occupations%20that%20require%20theoretical%20or%20technical%20expertise.%20Technology%20companies%20depend%20on%20it%20to%20hire%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20each%20year%20from%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recently%20determined%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20select%20additional%20registrations%20to%20reach%20the%20FY%202024%20numerical%20allocations.%20Soon%2C%20we%20will%20select%20additional%20registrations%20from%20previously%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20using%20a%20random%20selection%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20USCIS%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20announce%20once%20we%20have%20completed%20this%20second%20selection%20process%20and%20have%20notified%20all%20prospective%20petitioners%20with%20selected%20registrations%20from%20this%20round%20of%20selection%20that%20they%20are%20eligible%20to%20file%20an%20H-1B%20cap-subject%20petition%20for%20the%20beneficiary%20named%20in%20the%20applicable%20selected%20registration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20with%20selected%20registrations%20will%20have%20their%20accounts%20updated%20to%20include%20a%20selection%20notice%2C%20which%20includes%20details%20of%20when%20and%20where%20to%20file%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mandated%20by%20Congress%2C%20USCIS%20can%20issue%20a%20maximum%20of%2065%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20in%20a%20year.%20It%20can%20also%20issue%20another%2020%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20to%20foreign%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20higher%20studies%20from%20a%20US%20university%20in%20Science%2C%20Technol