%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325110%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20125%20students%20studying%20at%20minimal%20fees%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Lori%20Chauhan%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stayed%20in%20Sainji%20during%20the%20research%2C%20where%20she%20met%20her%20husband%20Kunwar%20Chauhan%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20village%20and%20introduced%20himself.%20He%20was%20educated%20in%20Delhi%20but%20chose%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20area.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20in%20common%20besides%20our%20care%20for%20the%20village%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESparks%20flew%20and%20the%20two%20got%20married%20in%202007%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20settled%20in%20Sainji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20a%20year%20into%20our%20marriage%2C%20many%20villagers%20would%20come%20and%20ask%20me%20if%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264558%2Fengineer-teaches-ipl-cricket-commentary-free-english-language-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20could%20teach%20English%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20children.%20Soon%2C%20they%20started%20requesting%20if%20we%20could%20start%20an%20English%20medium%20school%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20such%20requests%