%20very%20well%2C%20and%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20she%20does%20not%20get%20exhausted%20in%20the%20process.%20She%20is%20a%20very%20focused%20kid%20and%20even%20sacrifices%20her%20playtime%20sometimes%20to%20be%20on%20track%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20climbing%20the%20Everest%20Base%20Camp.%20Everyone%20at%20my%20school%2C%20especially%20my%20principal%2C%20was%20very%20supportive%20and%20permitted%20me%20to%20take%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20her%20friends%20responded%20to%20her%20achievements%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20did%20not%20think%20anything%20of%20it.%20But%20when%20I%20explained%20how%20big%20the%20mountain%20was%2C%20they%20got%20excited%20and%20felt%20proud%20of%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTraining%20a%20seven-year-old%20can%20be%20tricky%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20push%20them%20too%20hard.%20I%20sought%20advice%20from%20friends%20experienced%20in%20this%20area%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20prepare%20her%20for%20trekking%20high%20mountains.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20space%20or%20equipment%20and%20can%20start%20with%20simple%20exercises%20to%20build%20strength.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20high-intensity%20interval%20training%20too.%20Aadya%20was%20able%20to%20do%20the%20exercises%20effortlessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRunning%2C%20long%20walks%20with%20a%20five-kilo%20backpack%2C%20stair%20climbing%2C%20and%20smaller%20treks%20within%20Karnataka%20were%20a%20part%20of%20Aadya%E2%80%99s%20routine%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harsha%20decided%20to%20take%20her%20to%20the%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%2C%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20kind%20of%20reception%20he%20had%20hoped.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20including%20my%20family%2C%20parents%2C%20and%20friends%20said%20I%20was%20m