ant%20to%20help%20more%20mothers%20travel%20with%20their%20children%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20bloggers%20met%20on%20Instagram%20in%202019%20and%20got%20chatting.%20With%20a%20common%20profession%2C%20children%20of%20the%20same%20age%2C%20and%20a%20shared%20love%20for%20travel%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Montessori%20philosophy%2C%20the%20friendship%20was%20instant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20discuss%20a%20lot%20about%20varied%20topics.%20One%20day%2C%20we%20were%20speaking%20about%20how%20there%20are%20so%20many%20travel%20groups%20for%20women%2C%20solo%20travellers%2C%20senior%20citizens%2C%20couples%2C%20etc%2C%20but%20nothing%20for%20mothers%20and%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20they%20began%20discussing%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20travel%20group%20for%20mothers%20and%20their%20children%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20%E2%80%98Travel%20with%20Kids%20(India)%E2%80%99%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20and%20children%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20planned%20together%20was%20to%20Puducherry%20in%20October%202021.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20planned%20the%20first%20trip%20to%20Puducherry%20as%20I%20am%20very%20familiar%20with%20the%20place.%20We%20posted%20the%20trip%20details%20on%20our%20Instagram%20page%20and%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20two%20days.%20We%20took%20six%20moms%20and%20their%20children%20with%20us%2C%20and%20everyone%20had%20a%20great%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20since%20has%20been%20immense.%20With%20over%2075%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20today%2C%20the%20duo%20have%20planned%2020%20such%20trips%20across%20five%20destinations%20%E2%80%94%20P